Ko hono konga: * 78.084% meʻaloʻoa (naitolosena, N<sub>2</sub>) * 20.947% meʻaʻāsita (ʻosikena, O<sub>2</sub>) * 0.934% (Ar) * 0.033% malala-ongo-meʻaʻāsita (kāponika-ongo-ʻosikena, CO<sub>2</sub>) {{potuʻi}}
