Ko '''Sālote Mafileʻo Pilolevu''' ko e ʻalo fefine ia, ko e tuofefine ʻo e tuʻi, [[Siaosi Tupou V]]. ʻOku nonou: Pilinisesi Pilolevu.

Lolotonga 1984 ki he 1996 taimi ʻe niʻihi naʻe folau Pilolevu ki Aotealoa, naʻe ʻaʻahi ia kia [[Josh Liavaʻa]]. Naʻe pehē ʻa Josh ko [[Frederica Lupeʻuluiva Fatafehi ʻo Lapaha Tuita|Frederica]] ko ʻene ʻofefine moʻoni ia.<ref>Taimi ʻo Tonga & http://www.michaelfield.org/tonga7.htm</ref>
