Ko '''Titilupe Fanetupouvavaʻu Tuita''' ko e ʻalo fefine ia, ko e ʻilamutu ʻo e tuʻi, [[Siaosi Tupou V]]. ʻOku nonou: Pilinisesi Titilupe, pe Pilinisesi Fanetupouvavaʻu. Ko e kau ʻalo fefine ʻa Pilolevu, ʻoku toe ʻiloa: '''fuifuilupe'''.
