{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |hokohoko=Tukuʻao, SʻTN |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Sione Ngū Manumataongo Uelingatoni]] |faʻē= [[Melenaite Tupoumoheofo Veikune]] |ʻaho fanauʻi= 7 ʻOkatopa 1950 |ʻaho pekia= 5 Siulai 2006 |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Mele Siuʻilikutapu Kalaniuvalu (Tukuʻaho)]]|[[ʻElisiva Fusipala Taukiʻonetuku Namoa (Tukuʻaho)]]|||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Lavinia Mata-ʻo-Tāone Lausiʻi (Tukuʻaho)]]||[[Sinaitakala ʻOfeina ʻe he Langi Fakafānua (Tukuʻaho)]]|[[Viliami Tupoulahi Mailefihi Tukuʻaho]]||||||}} |ʻohoana1= [[Kaimana Hauoli ʻo Kuini Tukuʻaho (Aleamotuʻa)|Kaimana Hauoli ʻo Kuini Aleamotuʻa]] |ʻaho1= 28 Nōvema 1998 |fānau1={{tokoua|ʻikai||||||||}} |ʻohoana2=(sinifu) |fānau2={{tokoua|ʻOsaiasi Tuʻipulotu (1973—, foha ʻeveʻeva, nofo ʻAmelika)|Vakafuhu Tuʻifua (1994—, foha ʻeveʻeva, nofo Nuʻusila)|||||||}} |}}*http://www.matangitonga.to/article/tonganews/royalty/tu_ipelehake_legacy070706.shtml *Tonga investigation report
