{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= ʻUlukālala |ʻaho fakanofo= 1811 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= Maʻasi 1833 |ki muʻa=[[Fīnau ʻUlukālala II ʻi Feletoa (Fangupō)]] |hoko= [[Tupou Toutai Nafetalai Matekitonga]] |}} {{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Vavaʻu |ʻaho fakanofo= 1820 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= Maʻasi 1833 |ki muʻa=[[Fīnau ʻUlukālala II ʻi Feletoa (Fangupō)]] |hoko=[[Siaosi Tupou I|Tāufaʻāhau I]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama= tangata |tamai=[[Fīnau ʻUlukālala II ʻi Feletoa (Fangupō)]] |faʻē=Fatafehi Ongoʻalupe |ʻaho fanauʻi= |ʻaho pekia= Maʻasi 1833 |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Fīnau ʻUlukālala Moengangongo]]|[[Halaevalu Moheofo]]|||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1= [[Tuputupu ʻo Pulotu]] |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Fane Tupou Vavaʻu]]||||||||}} |ʻohoana2= [[Tupou Veiongo (Māʻatu)|Tupou Veiongo]] |fānau2= {{tokoua|[[Tupou Toutai Nafetalai Matekitonga]]||||||||}} |ʻohoana3= Siulolovao |ʻaho3= |fānau3= {{tokoua|Ane Tupou Falefehi||||||||}} |}}*http://web.archive.org/web/20030315012835/http://www.uq.net.au/~zzhsoszy/states/tonga/ulukalala.html
Naʻe ʻikai ʻalu ʻa e ʻUlukālala ʻia Fīnau Moengangongo neongo naʻe lahi, naʻe ʻalu ʻa e huafa ki hono tehina ko Fīnau Tuapasi. Naʻe ʻikai moʻui ʻa [[Takai]] ʻo aʻu ki he 1820, ko [[Tupoutoʻa (TK)|Tupoutoʻa]] pē ka naʻe ʻikai kau ia ai he ko ia ko e tehina ia ʻo ʻUlukālala II Feletoa (Fangupo) pea ko e ʻUlukālala ia naʻe Tuʻi Vavaʻu pea fietaʻa pea ilifiaʻi ʻi Tonga kotoa (kau ai ʻene fekau ʻa [[Tupouniua]] ke fakapoongi ʻa Tukuʻaho), ka naʻe lahi nofo ki Haʻapai pea ne taaʻi Port de au Prince ʻi he foʻiloto he matāfanga ʻo [[Lifuka|Koulo]] pea ne maʻu ai ʻa Tokiukamea Malina ʻo tauhi hono ʻohoana ko Mafihape.

