[[Image:Siaosi Tupou I motuʻa.jpg|right|220px|thumb|Siaosi I ʻi heʻene motuʻa]] {{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Vavaʻu |hingoa= Maeakafaua Tāufaʻāhau |hokohoko=Tupou I |ʻaho fakanofo= Maʻasi 1833 |ʻaho fakamālōlō=1865 |ki muʻa= [[Fīnau ʻUlukālala III ʻi Pouono (Tuapasi)]] |hoko= (liʻaki) |}} {{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Kanokupolu |hingoa= Tāufaʻāhau Tupou |hokohoko=Tupou I |ʻaho fakanofo= 4 Tisema 1845 |ʻaho pongipongi= 4 Tisema 1845 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= 18 Fēpueli 1893 |ki muʻa= [[Aleamotuʻa (Josiah Tupou)]] |hoko= [[Siaosi Tupou II]] |}} {{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi ʻo Tonga |hokohoko=Tupou I |ʻaho fakanofo= 4 Nōvema 1875 |ʻaho pongipongi= 4 Nōvema 1875 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= 18 Fēpueli 1893 |ki muʻa= (ʻuluaki tuʻi ʻo onopooni) |hoko= [[Siaosi Tupou II]] |}}
Hono hingoa faʻeleʻi naʻe '''Maeakafa Ngininginiofolanga'''. Hono hingoa fakatenetene mo fakamanakoʻanga naʻe '''Tāufaʻāhau'''. Naʻe maʻu ʻa e hingoa '''Tupou''' ʻi heʻene fakanofo ʻo e Tuʻi Kanokupolu. Pea naʻe maʻu ʻa e hingoa '''Siaosi''' (meia George III, tuʻi ʻo Pilitānia), ʻosi ʻene papi fakakalisitiane. ʻOku toe ʻa e huafa tenetene ko '''Lopa ʻaione''' pe '''Lopa ukamea''' (ngalingali mei he Maea-kafa). ʻI he lea fakatonga onoʻaho: '''...Giniginiofolaga... Jiaoji Tubou'''. Ko e ʻaho mo e feituʻu ʻo ʻene fāʻeleʻi ʻoku ʻikai ʻiloa. Kā naʻe ʻikai he 4 Tisema, ko e hisitolia ʻi Niuʻui ʻi [[Tongoleleka]]. Mahalo pe ofi ki [[Koloua]] ʻi Tongatapu ka 'oku 'ikai fakapapau'i ia.{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |hokohoko=Tupou I |hingoa=Maeakafaua Ngininginiofolanga Tāufaʻāhau (Siaosi Tupou I) |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Tupoutoʻa (TK)|Tupoutoʻa]] |faʻē= [[Tāufa Hoamofaleono]] |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1797 |ʻaho pekia= pālasi, 18 Fēpueli 1893 |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Luseane Halaevalu Mataʻaho]]|[[Fīnau Filimoeʻulie]]|[[Fifita Holeva]]||||||}} |ʻohoana1= Fīnau Kaunanga |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Sālote Mafileʻo Pilolevu (Tupou)]]||||||||}} |ʻohoana2= Kalolaine Fusimatalili |fānau2= {{tokoua|[[Tēvita ʻUnga]]||||||||}} |ʻohoana3= Pasikole |fānau3= {{tokoua|[[ʻIsileli Tupou]]|Mafi ʻAkanesi|||||||}} |ʻohoana4= [[Sālote Lupepauʻu]] |ʻaho4= 1834 |fānau4= {{tokoua|[[Tuʻuakitau]]|[[Vuna Takitakimālohi]]|||||||}} |}}
ʻOku ne tōfā ʻi [[Malaʻekula]].

