{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Kanokupolu |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1775? |ʻaho pongipongi= mahalo pē ʻikai |ʻaho fakamālōlō= 1782 |ki muʻa=[[Maealiuakimuʻa]] |hoko=[[Tupoulahisiʻi]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama= tangata |tamai=[[Tupoulahimuʻa]] |faʻē= [[Fuonuku]] |ʻaho fanauʻi= 1747 |ʻaho pekia= 1790 |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|Tongamana Tupouhaʻapai|[[Tupoumoheofo]]|||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1=[[ʻUheina]] |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Tupoulahisiʻi]]|[[Tupoumālohi]]|[[Tupoufalemei]]||||||}} |}}*I.C. Campbell, Island kingdom, Canterbury university press, 1992, 2001 * E. Bott; Tonga society at the time of Captain Cook's visit; 1982 Naʻe ui ia ko ''Fīnau'' ʻe he ʻeikivaka Semisi Kuki. Mahalo pē ʻoku fakapuputuʻu ia mo [[Fīnau ʻUlukālala I ʻi Maʻofanga]]
Mahalo pē naʻe ʻikai ʻaupito ʻe hoko Tuʻi Kanokupolu, kā naʻe folau ki [[Fisi]] pē. Mahalo pē foki ko Tupoumālohi naʻe ʻikai hono foha pea mo ohi ia ʻe [[Mumui Tupouʻila Mapatongiamanu]], kā ko e foha moʻoni ʻo Mumui.

