{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki
|maama= tangata
|tamai=[[Mumui Tupouʻila Mapatongiamanu]]
|faʻē= [[Sele Lepolo]] (ʻofefine ʻo Atafakahau (Ata II))
|ʻaho fanauʻi= 1753
|ʻaho pekia=21 ʻEpeleli 1799
|taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Halaevalu (TK)|Halaevalu]]||||||||}}
|taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;||||||||}} 
|tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Halaevalu Fonongavaʻinga]]|[[Tupou Veiongo]]|Uipulotumatāpule|[[Tupoumālohi]]|[[Aleamotuʻa (Josiah Tupou)]]|Namoa|||}}
|ʻohoana1= [[ʻUlukilupetea]]
|fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Tupoutoʻa (TK)|Tupoutoʻa]]||||||||}}
|ʻohoana2= [[Halaevalu (TK)|Halaevalu]]
|fānau2= {{tokoua|[[Ulakai]]||||||||}}
|ʻohoana3= (taʻeʻiloa)
|fānau3= {{tokoua|[[Fusipala Taukiʻonetuku]]||||||||}}
|ʻohoana4= [[ʻAmelia Fakahikuʻoʻuiha]]
|fānau4=
|}}
Ko e kōvana ʻo ʻEua ia ʻi 1793. Naʻe tau ia kia [[Tupoumoheofo]], kae naʻe ikai maʻu ia ko e huafa Tuʻi Kanokupolu ʻi he taimi ko ia. Ko e tangata angafakamamahi mo e taʻmoʻoni ia. Naʻe tāmateʻi ʻia ʻe [[Fīnau ʻUlukālala II ʻi Feletoa (Fangupō)]] mo hono tehina Tupouniua.

Ko hono hingoa lōloa ko '''Fīnau Tukuʻaho'''. Naʻa ne liliu ki he huafa '''Taliai Tupou''' ʻosi ʻene fakanofo.

