{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Vavaʻu |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1750? |ʻaho fakamālōlō= ~1777? |ki muʻa= (ʻuluaki) |hoko= [[Fīnau ʻUlukālala I ʻi Maʻofanga]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Mataelehaʻamea]] |faʻē= Talaumoteʻemoa |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1700 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Maʻafuʻotuʻitonga]]|[[Tupoutoʻa]]|[[Fusipala]]|Hahanokifangaʻuta|[[Halaevalu]]|Kafoa|[[Tongotea]]||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1= Lātūfuipeka |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Fīnau ʻUlukālala I ʻi Maʻofanga]]||||||||}} |ʻohoana2= Ngalu |fānau2= {{tokoua|[[Fīnau Pasiaka]]||||||||}} |ʻohoana3= Melesilika Tulukava |fānau3= {{tokoua|[[Fīnau Pipiki]]||||||||}} |}}*http://epress.anu.edu.au/austronesians/origins/mobile_devices/ch12s03.html Ko hono tuofefine ko [[Fusipala]] naʻe liua ʻe ia ʻa e hau ʻo e [[:Category:Tuʻi Vavaʻu|Tuʻi Vavaʻu]] ko Vuna Tuʻiʻoetau, pea naʻe hoko ʻa Tuituiohu ko e hau (naʻe talataha ʻe Fusipala).
Naʻe kamata ha holongā hau foʻou. Hono hako ʻoku ʻiloa ko e [[:Category:Haʻa Ngata Tupu|Haʻa Ngata Tupu]].

