Nofo ʻi [[Niuafoʻou]]

{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Kanokupolu
|ʻaho fakanofo= ~1700
|ʻaho fakamālōlō=
|ki muʻa= [[Mataelehaʻamea]]
|hoko= [[Maʻafuʻotuʻitonga]]
|}}

{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki
|maama= tangata
|tamai=[[Mataeletuʻapiko]]
|faʻē= Papa (ʻofefine ʻo Aokatoa, ko e Tuʻihaʻamea)
|ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1700
|ʻaho pekia=
|taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Mataelehaʻamea]]||||||||}}
|taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;||||||||}} 
|tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Afualo]]|[[Vaivai]]|[[Hafoka]]||||||}}
|ʻohoana1=?
|fānau1= {{tokoua|?||||||||}}
|}}
Naʻe hoko ia ko e kōvana ʻo [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]]. Naʻe feinga ia ʻo kamata ʻa e holongā  hau ʻi hē, ko e [[:Category:Tuʻi Vavaʻu|Tuʻi Vavaʻu]], kae naʻe ʻikai ikuna, koeʻuhi naʻe ʻikai mali ia mo e taʻahine Vavaʻu, pea mo naʻe feinga ʻa e meʻa tatau ʻe [[Tuituiohu]]. ʻAmui naʻe hoko ia ko e Tuʻi Kanokupolu, naʻe fetongi ia hono taʻokete.

{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Kanokupolu
|ʻaho fakanofo= ~1675
|ʻaho fakamālōlō= 
|ki muʻa= [[Mataeletuʻapiko]]
|hoko= [[Vuna Tuʻiʻoetau]]
|}}

{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki
|maama= tangata
|tamai= [[Mataeletuʻapiko]]
|faʻē= Papa
|ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1675
|ʻaho pekia=
|taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}}
|taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} 
|tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Vuna Tuʻiʻoetau]]|[[Afualo]]|[[Vaivai]]|[[Hafoka]]|||||}}
|ʻohoana1= [[Kaloafutonga (TH)|Kaloafutonga]]
|fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Maʻafuʻotuʻitonga]]|[[Tupoutoʻa]]|[[Fusipala]]||||||}}
|ʻohoana2= Humi
|fānau2= {{tokoua||Hahanokifangaʻuta|[[Halaevalu]]|Kafoa|[[Tongotea]]|||||}}
|ʻohoana3= Talaumoteomoa
|fānau3= {{tokoua|[[Tuituiohu]]|||||||||}}
|}}
Mahalo pē naʻe tau ia kia [[Vaea]], kae naʻe mali ia hono ʻofefine.

Hono tehina ko Vuna, naʻe hoko ia ko e kōvana ʻo [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]].

Hono tehina ko Hafoka, naʻe hoko ia ko e kōvana ʻo vahe loto ʻo [[Tongatapu]]. Naʻe kamata ia ʻa e holongā hau foʻou, ko e [[:Category:Haʻa Havea lahi|Haʻa Havea lahi]]. ʻI he kahaʻu naʻe hoko ʻa e haʻá ni mo e [[:Category:Tuʻi Kanokupolu|Tuʻi Kanokupolu]] ʻena fili.

ʻOku ui foki ko '''Mataele ʻusitea''', ko e ʻuhinga naʻe ʻikai tātatau ʻi hono tuʻa.

