{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua
|ʻaho fakanofo= ~1575
|ʻaho fakamālōlō= 
|ki muʻa= [[Vakalahimoheʻuli]]
|hoko= [[Fotofili]]
|}}

{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki
|maama= tangata
|tamai= [[Vakalahimoheʻuli]]
|faʻē=
|ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1575
|ʻaho pekia=
|taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}}
|taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} 
|tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Vaʻetuʻikoloa]]|[[Vaoloa]]|[[Tauʻatevalu]]||||||}}
|ʻohoana1= [[Tohuʻia Limapō]]
|fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Fotofili]]|Niukapu|Nuku|[[Ngata]]|[[Kaloafūtonga]]|||||}}
|ʻohoana2= Holokuku
|fānau2= {{tokoua|[[Lāvaka Haʻatuʻukau]]|||||||||}}
|}}
Naʻa ne taʻane mo e fineʻeiki mei [[Haʻamoa]], neongo naʻe ngofua pē ia maʻa e [[:Category:Tuʻi Tonga|Tuʻi Tonga]]. Naʻe hiki ki ʻolunga pehē ʻa e [[mana]] ʻo e Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua.

Ko hono foha ʻuluaki, naʻe hoko ko e Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua hoko. Ko e hoko, Niukapu, naʻe hoko ia ʻe heʻene ʻeiki ko e kōvana ʻo Haʻapai. Ko e hoko, Nuku, naʻe hoko ia ko e kōvana ʻo Hahake, ko e vahe fonua lahi mo e koloaʻia. Pea ko e mui, Ngata, naʻe hoko ia ko e kōvana ʻo vahe Hihifo pē, siʻi mo e masiva. Naʻe mateʻi ʻe ha tokotaha ʻe hoko ʻa e hako ʻo Ngata ki he holongā tuʻi mālohi taha? ʻOku hifo Niukapu mo Nuku he taimí ni, ʻoku na kau ki he [[:Category:Haʻa Lātūhifo|Haʻa Lātūhifo]].

Mahalo pē ko ''Nuku'' ʻoku ʻikai hono foha, ka ko e foha ʻo hono tehina, ko ''Vaoloa'', ko hono huafa ko [[Nuku ʻUlutolu]].

Ko '''Tauʻatevalu''' ko e ʻuluaki [[Valu]] ia ʻo [[ʻUtulau]]
{{English|translation}}
*E.W. Gifford, Tongan Society, BPB museum bulletin 61, 1929

