Ko e kiʻi palopalema. Kapau naʻe moʻui Lupemeitakui ʻi he teautaʻu hono 17, fefē Tupoulahimuʻa ʻi he teautaʻu hono 18 ? Mahalo pē ko Lupemeitakui naʻa ne taʻane mo Tupoulahimuʻa pea mo Maealiuakimuʻa, ko Lupemeitakui kehe ia mo e ʻofefine ʻo Tungīmānaʻia mo Takala.

Pe ko hono hingoa totonu ko '''Lupematakui''' ?
*E.W. Gifford, Tongan Society, BPB museum bulletin 61, 1929

