{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tamahā |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1650 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Tuʻimala]] |hoko= [[Moʻungaolakepa]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga= houʻeiki |maama= fefine |tamai=[[Tungīmānaʻia]] |faʻē= [[Sinaitakalaʻilotunofo]] |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1650 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[ʻUluakimata II]]|[[Totonukuoʻosi]]|[[Hokoʻiamailangi]]||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Lātūtama]]|[[Mapa (THT)|Mapa]]|[[Lupemeitakui]]|Tahi|||||}} |ʻohoana1= [[Vaea]] |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Moeakiola]]||||||||}} |}}*E.W. Gifford; Tongan society; 1929 ʻOku ʻikai hā totonu ʻa e tamahā ʻe [[Sālote Tupou III]], kae hono tama, Moeakiola, naʻe Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua hoko.
Naʻe moʻui ʻanefē? Ko e toenga ʻo hono kāinga naʻe moʻui ~1725. Kae Vaea mo Moeakiola naʻe moʻui ~1650. Mahalo pe naʻa ne taʻane ki ha Vaea kehe?

