{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1470 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= (ʻuluaki ia) |hoko= [[Tānekingaʻotonga]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Takalaua]] |faʻē= Vaʻelaveamata (ʻUlukihelupe) |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1470 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Kauʻulufonua (fekai)]]||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|Melinoʻatonga|Lotauai|Lātūtoevave||||||}} |ʻohoana1=? |fānau1= {{tokoua|Tāufatofua|[[Tānekingaʻotonga]]|||||||}} |}}* E.W. Gifford, Tongan myths and tales, BPB '''8''', 1924
Ko hono foha ʻuluaki, ko Tāufatofua, naʻe hoko kōvana ʻo [[Tofua]]. Ko e fānau mo e makapuna ʻa Takalaua naʻe hoko kinautolu ʻa e tupuʻa ʻo e ngaahi kāinga ʻo e [[:Category:Haʻa Takalaua|Haʻa Takalaua]], fakatātā: [[:Category:Takalaua|Takalaua]], [[:Category:Moʻungāmotuʻa|Moʻungāmotuʻa]], [[:Category:Melino-ʻa-Tonga|Melino-ʻa-Tonga]], [[:Category:Lotauai|Lotauai]], [[:Category:Tāufatofua|Tāufatofua]], mo e [[:Category:Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua|Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua]] meia Tānekingaʻotonga.
ʻOku pehē ʻe [[Niel Gunson]] naʻe ʻafifio ʻa e [[:Category:Tuʻi Tonga|Tuʻi Tonga]] ʻi he taimi ko ia ʻi [[Manuʻa]] pea naʻa nau hoko ki he [[Tuʻi Manuʻa]]. Ko ia ai ʻoku hala ha tuʻi ʻi Tongatapu, pea naʻe kamata ha holongā tuʻi foʻou. *http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m2375/is_n2_v32/ai_20554487/pg_6 {{English|abstract}}

{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Tonga |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1470 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Takalaua]] |hoko= [[Vakafuhu]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Takalaua]] |faʻē= [[Vaʻelaveamata]] |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1470 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Moʻungāmotuʻa]]|Melinoʻatonga|Lotauai|Lātūtoevave|||||}} |ʻohoana1=? |fānau1= {{tokoua|Fotofili|[[Vakafuhu]]|||||||}} |}}* E.W. Gifford, Tongan myths and tales, BPB '''8''', 1924 Naʻe tuli ʻe Kauʻulufonua mo e hono fanga tehina ʻa e ongo tangata fakapō ʻo e ʻene ʻeiki ki [[Tongatapu]], [[ʻEua]], [[:category:Haʻapai|Haʻapai]], [[:category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]], [[Niuafoʻou]], [[Niuatoputapu]], [[Haʻamoa]], [[Futuna]], pea mo [[ʻUvea]]. ʻI he fonua ē, naʻe hamu Tamasia mo Molofafa ʻe he tuʻi fekai.
Ko hono foha ʻuluaki, ko Fotofili, naʻe kōvana ʻo Niuafoʻou. Kae māhalo pē naʻe hala ʻa e motuʻa ʻi heʻene talanoa. Ko [[:category:Fotofili|Fotofili]] moʻoni, ko ha tokotaha kehe ia.
ʻI he ngaahi talatupufonua mei [[Haʻamoa]] ko e foha ʻe 3 ʻo ''Faisautele'' (Kauʻulufonua) ko Tuiaviʻi mo To[n]gialelei mo [[Puipuifatu]] kinautolu.
*E.W. Gifford, Tongan Society, BPB museum bulletin 61, 1929 {{English|abstract}}

{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Tonga |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1450 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Havea II]] |hoko= [[Kauʻulufonua (fekai)]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Havea II]] |faʻē= |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1450 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1= [[Vaʻelaveamata]] |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Kauʻulufonua (fekai)]]|[[Moʻungāmotuʻa]]|Melinoʻatonga|Lotauai|Lātūtoevave||||}} |}}*E.W. Gifford, Tongan myths and tales, Bernice Pauahi Bishop museum bulletin '''8''', 1924 ʻI he talanoa kehe, ko Lātūtoevave ʻoku ui Lātūteovave, pea ko e taʻokete ia ʻo Melinoʻatonga mo Lotauai.
Naʻe moemoepō ʻa Takalaua ʻe he ongo tamasiʻi mei [[ʻUvea]], ko Tamasia mo Malofafa, lolotonga ʻene taumafa ʻi he motu ʻo [[Mataʻaho (Tongatapu)|Mataʻaho]]. Pe, ʻi he tala kehe, naʻa ne moemoepō ʻi Fangafeʻatu, ʻi he matātahi ʻo [[Talasiu]] ʻe he ongo tamasiʻi mei [[Pelehake]]. {{English|translation}}

