{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Tonga |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1250 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Talaihaʻapepe]] |hoko= [[Talafāpite]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Talaihaʻapepe]] |faʻē= |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1250 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1=? |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Talafāpite]]||||||||}} |}} Naʻe ikuna ʻa e kau toa fakahaʻamoa ʻi he tau mo Tonga. Naʻa nau ʻikuʻi he Tuʻi Tonga koʻeni. ʻI heʻene hola mei [[Tualatala]] ʻi [[Haʻamoa]] naʻe pehē ʻe Talakaifaiki (Talaʻifeiʻi ʻi he [[lea fakahaʻamoa]]): Mālie toa, mālie tau afai ou te toe sau ou te sau i le aouliuli folau ae lē ʻo le aouliuli tau!
Mālie toʻa, mālie tau ʻoka te u toe haʻu te u haʻu ʻi he liu folau kae ʻikai ko e liu tau!
{{English|translation}}

