Ko hono hingoa ko '''ʻIlaheva''' ia, kae naʻa ne nofo ofi ki Vaʻepopua ʻi Tongatapu. ʻEne ʻeiki mahalo pē naʻe nofo ʻi Tongatapu, māhalo pē ʻi Niutoputapu, pe Niuē pe Haʻamoa.
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki
|maama= fefine
|tamai= [[Seketoʻa]]
|faʻē=
|ʻaho fanauʻi= ~900
|ʻaho pekia=
|taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}}
|taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} 
|tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}}
|ʻohoana1= [[Tangaloa ʻEitumātupuʻa]]
|fānau1= {{tokoua|[[ʻAhoʻeitu]]||||||||}}
|}}*E.W. Gifford; ''Tongan myths and tales'', BPB Bulletin '''8'''; 1924

