*I.C. Campbell, Island kingdom, Canterbury university press, 1992, 2001

Naʻe ʻafio ʻa Vakafuhu ʻi Haʻamoa. Mahalo pē ko Vakafuhu, tamai ʻo e ʻotua-ika ko Tuʻitofua, ko e tokotaha kehe ia.{{English|abstract}}

{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Tonga |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1520 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Vakafuhu]] |hoko= [[Kauʻulufonua II ]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Vakafuhu]] |faʻē= |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1520 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1=? |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Kauʻulufonua II ]]||||||||}} |}}*http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m2375/is_n2_v32/ai_20554487/pg_4 Naʻa ne ʻafio ʻi [[Haʻamoa]] ([[Manuʻa]]) pea ko [[:Category:Tuʻiʻāfitu|Tuʻiʻāfitu]] ko hono hako. Naʻe feinga ia foki ki Tonga, kae ʻikai ikunaʻi ʻi Vavaʻu.
Naʻe tala mai ʻi [[Haʻamoa]] ko Puipuifatu ko e foha ʻo [[Kauʻulufonua (fekai)]] mo Taufaitoa. {{English|abstract}}

{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Tonga |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1540 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Puipuifatu]] |hoko= [[Tapuʻosi]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Puipuifatu]] |faʻē= |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1540 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1=Taupouimasina (Taupoʻou-ʻi-māhina) |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Tapuʻosi]]|Vaʻetoeʻifanga|||||||}} |}} Naʻe ʻafio ʻi Haʻamoa ia.
Naʻe tala mai ʻi [[Haʻamoa]] ko Kauʻulufonua II ko e foha ʻo [[Kauʻulufonua (fekai)]] mo Vainuʻulasi (Vainukulahi). *E.W. Gifford, Tongan Society, BPB museum bulletin 61, 1929

{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Tonga |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1560 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Kauʻulufonua II]] |hoko= [[ʻUluakimata I]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Kauʻulufonua II]] |faʻē=Taupouimasina (Taupoʻou-ʻi-māhina) |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1560 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1=Vaʻenopo |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[ʻUluakimata I]]||||||||}} |}}* I.C. Campbell, Island kingdom, Canterbury university press, 1992, 2001 Ko e Tuʻi Tonga koʻeni naʻe foki ki Tongí ni. ʻIkai tatau mo e hau, ko e hau moʻoni ko e [[:category:Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua|Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua]] ia ([[Siulangapō]] pe [[Vakalahimoheʻuli]]), kae mei he taimi ē ʻoku meimei tatau ʻa e Tuʻi Tonga mo ha ʻotua.
Vaʻenopo: ko e ʻofefine ʻo Lāvakavaoleleva ko e tehina ʻo ʻAhomeʻe; ko e ʻofefine ʻo ʻAhomeʻe [Bastian]; tatau mo Va`etapu, ʻofefine ʻo ʻAhomeʻe [hokohoko ʻo Tamahā]. {{English|abstract}} *E.W. Gifford, Tongan Society, BPB museum bulletin 61, 1929

