ʻOku ui foki ko '''Tuʻipulotu II'''. Ko hono huafa lōloa ko e ʻuhinga naʻa ne telio ʻi he langi Tuʻoteau. 

ʻOku toe lahi ʻene sinifu: Tuʻilokamana mo Tangaloa mo Tupoutaʻanea mo Fakatoumafi mo Lāpulou mo Hafuni...

{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Tonga |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1750 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Tuʻipolutuʻilangituʻoteau]] |hoko= [[Maʻulupekotofa]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Tuʻipolutuʻilangituʻoteau]] |faʻē= [[Laumanakilupe]] |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1750 |ʻaho pekia= 1789 |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Maʻulupekotofa]]||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Siumafuaʻuta]]|Talaumokafoa|||||||}} |ʻohoana1= [[Tupoumoheofo]] |ʻaho1= ~1765 |fānau1= {{tokoua|Fatafehi Haʻapai|Fatafehi Lapaha|Manutauhakau|[[Fatafehi Fuanunuiava]]|[[Sinaitakalaʻifekitetele]]||||}} |}}
[[File:Palatavake.jpg|right|300px|thumb|Ko e palatavake]]
ʻOku ui '''Paulaho''' ʻe he ʻeikivaka [[Semisi Kuki]]. Naʻe ʻoatu ʻe Pau ʻa e palatavake ongoongoa faʻu ʻe [[Havea Hikuleʻo Helu]].
Ko e meʻa fakaofo heni: ko Pau naʻe ʻikai ko e tama ʻo e moheofo, tatau mo Siumafuaʻuta. *I.C. Campbell, Island kingdom, Canterbury university press, 1992, 2001

