Naʻa ne fakafisi (?) mei he Tuʻi Tonga ʻi 1795, kae hala ʻi 1806. Naʻe tala ʻe [[Tokiukamea]] naʻe telio ʻa e Tuʻi Tonga he 2 Tisema 1806, ʻi he ʻaho hono 2 ʻo heʻene nofo ʻi Tonga. ʻI he ʻaho ko ia, naʻe kosiʻuluʻi kakai kotoa pē.
*J. Martin; Tonga islands, William Mariner's account; 1817
{{English|translation}}

