{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo
|maama= tangata
|tamai= [[Pau]]
|faʻē= [[Tupoumoheofo]]
|ʻaho fanauʻi= 1765
|ʻaho pekia= 1810
|taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|Fatafehi Haʻapai|Fatafehi Lapaha|Manutauhakau||||||}}
|taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;||||||}} 
|tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Sinaitakalaʻifekitetele]]||||||||}}
|ʻohoana1= [[Tupou Veiongo]]
|fānau1= {{tokoua||[[Sanualio Laufilitonga]]|||||||}}
|ʻohoana2= [[Tupoufalemei]]
|fānau2= {{tokoua||[[Kavafutuna]]|||||||}}
|}}
Naʻe ʻi ai ha kātonga lahi ʻi 1777, naʻe sio ʻe he ʻeikivaka Semisi Kuki, ko e nofoʻanga ʻo Fuanunuiava ki he huafa ʻalo Tuʻi Tonga. Ko e hā e ʻuhinga? Mahalo pē ko Tupoumoheofo, ko e [[moheofo]] ia naʻe ʻikai ʻene fehuhu, kā ko ʻene fehuhu, ko ha fokonofo pē ʻo Pau, ko Inumofalefā ia.

Naʻa ne ʻafio ʻi [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]], koeʻuhi ʻa e tau ʻi Tongatapu. Naʻe tala ʻe [[Tokiukamea]] ko e taʻane ʻo Fuanunuiava mo e ʻofefine (ko Popua ?) ʻo 
[[Fīnau ʻUlukālala II ʻi Feletoa (Fangupō)]].

[[File:Laufilitonga cross.jpg|right|300px|thumb|Ko e kolosi ʻi ʻolunga ʻo e [[ʻotu langi|langi Tu‘ofefafa]] ʻo ʻene tōfāʻanga. Ko e kiʻi sila ʻi he lotomālie ʻo e kolosi ʻoku pehē: KUO TELIO ENI I HON[O] 11 O TESIMA [sic] 1865 AE TUI TOGA KO SANUALIO LAUFILITOGA KUO PEKIA IA Y [sic] HONO 9. MOU HUFAKI IA]] {{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻi Tonga |ʻaho fakanofo= 1827 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= 1865 |ki muʻa= [[Fatafehi Fuanunuiava]] |hoko= (ngataʻanga) |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=fale ʻalo |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Fatafehi Fuanunuiava]] |faʻē= [[Tupou Veiongo]] |ʻaho fanauʻi= 24 ʻAokosi 1797 |ʻaho pekia= 9 Tisema 1865 |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1= [[Lātūniua]] |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Manumataongo]]|[[Fakauakimanuka]]|||||||}} |ʻohoana2= [[Luseane Halaevalu Mataʻaho]] |fānau2= {{tokoua|[[Viliami Kalaniuvalu]]|[[Lavinia Veiongo (māhanga)]]|||||||}} |ʻohoana3= [[Lātū Fakahau]] |fānau3= {{tokoua|[[Hepisipa]]||||||||}} |ʻohoana4= [[Siulolovao]] |fānau4= {{tokoua|[[Fatafehi Fangaʻafā]]||||||||}} |}}*E. Wood-Ellem, Queen Sālote of Tonga, Auckland university press, 1999 Naʻe tala ange ʻe [[Tokiukamea]] ko e tamasiʻi ia, taʻu ʻe 15 pe ofi ki ai ʻi he taimi ʻo heʻene mavahe mei Vavaʻu ʻi 1810.
Kuo taʻane ʻa Laufilitonga mo e kau fefine ʻe 18 tupu, kā ʻoku ʻoatu heni e tokonima pē. ʻOku toe ʻa hano ʻohoana mahuʻinga ʻe taha: ko [[Sālote Lupepauʻu]], kā naʻe ʻikai haʻana fānau. Ko [[Luseane Halaevalu Mataʻaho]], ko e ʻofefine ʻo e [[:Category:Tuʻi Kanokupolu|Tuʻi Kanokupolu]], naʻe kohuʻi ʻa e ʻohoana mahuʻinga taha, ko e [[moheofo]]. Kae naʻe ʻikai ha taupoʻou, koeʻuhi ʻa e kākā ʻo [[Siaosi Tupou I|Tāufaʻāhau]].
Ko e niʻini ʻo e toenga ʻo e kau sinifu mo e fokonofo kinautolu: *[[Moʻungaʻulufeholoi]] *[[ Susana Motulalo]], fānau: Fusipala Pangai
Ko e Tuʻi Tonga fakaʻosi ia, kae ʻe fakanofo ʻa hono foha ʻi he hingoa nōpele ko e [[:category:Kalaniuvalu|Kalaniuvalu]] ʻe [[Siaosi Tupou I]]. Kae naʻe fieʻoatu ʻe Laufilitonga ʻa e mafai ʻo e Tuʻi Tonga ki hono ʻilamutu, ko [[Siaosi Fatafehi Toutaitokotaha]] ([[:category:Tuʻipelehake|Tuʻipelehake]]), (mokopuna ʻo ʻene fehuhu [[Tupou Veiongo]] mo e ʻeiki kehekehe).
He ʻaho 7 Nōvema 1851, naʻa ne papitaiso ʻi he [[siasi Katolika Loma]], naʻa ne liliu hono huafa kia '''Samuelio Fatafehi Laufilitonga''' (ka ʻoku tohi ko Sanualio Laufilitonga). {{English|translation}}

'''Articles awaiting to be translated in Tongan'''

That is very, very bad. The English version of the articles mentioned on the previous page is more elaborate than the Tongan. There must be somebody who wants to translate them into Tongan. Who is able to, and takes up the challenge?
{{Foki|f|Ngaahi kupu tali liliu ʻi he lea fakatonga}}

Queen Sālote Tupou III got 3 living sons, and after that she had 3 miscarriages.
{{Foki||Sālote Tupou III}}

For more in English, see [[:en:Salote Tupou III of Tonga]].

