Naʻe pau ʻe hoko ʻa e [[moheofo]] ko Luseane. Kae naʻe ʻikai fieloto ki ai ʻa hono tuongaʻane, ko [[Siaosi Tupou I|Tāufaʻāhau]], koeʻuhi ko [[Laufilitonga]] ko hono fili ia. Ko ia ai, naʻe fekau ʻuluaki ʻe Tāufaʻāhau ʻa hono tuofefine ki he [[:Category:Tuʻihaʻateiho|Tuʻihaʻateiho]]. ʻOsi ʻene fāʻele, naʻe fekau ia ki he [[:Category:Tuʻi Tonga|Tuʻi Tonga]]. Kae naʻe ʻikai kei taupoʻou, naʻe ʻikai te ne lava fāʻele ha hako kia te ia.
