{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo=Māʻatu |ʻaho fakanofo= |ʻaho fakamālōlō= ~1830 ? |ki muʻa=[[Kulīhaʻapai]] |hoko=[[Ngongo]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama=tangata |tamai=[[Kulīhaʻapai]] |faʻē= [[Kavafutuna]] |ʻaho fanauʻi=~1750 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1= [[Lātūtama (Māʻatu)|Lātūtama]] |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Ngongo]]|[[Tupou Veiongo (Māʻatu)|Tupou Veiongo]]||||||||}} |}}*E. Wood-Ellem, Queen Sālote of Tonga, Auckland university press, 1999 *http://kitwithers.fortunecity.com/tonga/nobles.html *E.W. Gifford, Tongan Society, BPB museum bulletin 61, 1929
Naʻa nau folau, ko Ikamāfana mo hono fānau ko Ngongo mo Veiongo, ki [[ʻUvea]]. Naʻa ne fakapoongi ʻi ai, pea naʻe nonofo pē ʻi ʻUvea ʻa e ongo fānau. Naʻe ohi ʻa Ngongo ʻe he ʻofefine ʻo e tuʻi ʻo ʻUvea pea naʻe ʻikai te tāmateʻi ʻa e toenga ʻo e kakai folau.

