{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuʻivakanō |ʻaho fakanofo= |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= (ʻuluaki ia) |hoko= [[Manuʻatua Tuʻivakanō]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi |faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Mataeletuʻapiko]] |faʻē= ʻUmukisia |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1825 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1=? |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Manuʻatua Tuʻivakanō]]||||||||}} |ʻohoana2=? |fānau2= {{tokoua|[[ʻAnaseini Tokilupe ʻEveʻevaʻitoafa Kaho]]||||||||}} |}}
Naʻe tala mai ko e foha ia ʻo [[Mataeletuʻapiko]], ko e [[:Category:Tuʻi Kanokupolu|Tuʻi Kanokupolu]] fika 3 ia. Ka naʻa ne moʻui taʻu ʻe 200 tupu ki muʻa. Mahalo pē ha Aokatoa kehe, ko e tangata [[Fisi]] mei [[Lakeba]] ʻoku ui foko ko e '''Tuʻisoso'''. Naʻa ne mali mo Huiʻuha, ko e ongo foha ko e ongo Tuʻivakanō hoko, ko Mafana mo Hafokameʻe. Hoko ko Hafokameʻe II, hoko ko e tokotaha, hoko ko Fā. *E.W. Gifford, Tongan Society, BPB museum bulletin 61, 1929
Ko Uiliami Aokatoa ke ʻeiki ʻo [[Nukunuku]] ia. Naʻe ʻita ʻa hono kāinga koeʻuhi ʻene fakalotuʻi pea nau angatuʻu ʻi he kolotau ko [[Hule]]. Naʻe kole ʻe Aokatoa kia [[Siaosi Tupou I|Tāufaʻāhau]] ke ne tokoni mai, ke ne ikuna. Naʻe ikuʻi ʻa Hule ʻe ia ʻi 1826 pe ofi ki ai.

