{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuita |ʻaho fakanofo= |ʻaho pongipongi= |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Upolutele Tuita]] ? |hoko= [[Poʻoi Niutupuʻivaha]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Upolutele Tuita]] |faʻē= [[ʻĀnaukihesina]] |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1775 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |ʻohoana1=[[Lātūfuipeka]] |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Makahokovalu]]|[[Lātūniua]]|[[Vuki]]|Lātūolaʻifotuika|Lātūʻotusia||||}} |ʻohoana2=[[Fīnaukovi]] |fānau2= {{tokoua|[[Poʻoi Niutupuʻivaha]]|Lataitokelau|Noaʻisiapua|Nunufaʻikea|Faingaʻanuku||||}} |ʻohoana3=Tausisi |fānau3= {{tokoua|Tupoukenutu|Sioana|||||||}} |}}*http://www.planet-tonga.com/forums/viewtopic.php?t=12628&postdays=0&postorder=asc&start=30 *http://freepages.genealogy.rootsweb.com/~royalty/tonga/i288.html#I288 *http://epress.anu.edu.au/austronesians/origins/mobile_devices/ch12s02.html ʻI he taimi ko ia naʻe māʻulalo pē ʻa e hingoa [[:Category:Tuita|Tuita]], ʻoku ʻikai feʻunga maʻa e foha ʻo e [[:Category:Tuʻi Tonga Fefine|Tuʻi Tonga Fefine]], ko Makahokovalu. ʻA ia, naʻe fakanofoʻi ʻa Poʻoi mo e hingoá. Kae ʻosi ʻene pekia, naʻe foki ʻa e hingoa ki he foha ʻo Makahokovalú.
ʻI heʻene motuʻa mo kui, naʻa ne folau ʻi he vaka ʻo [[Sanualio Laufilitonga]] mei [[Haʻamoa]] foki ki Tonga. Ke naʻe heeʻi ʻa e vaka. Pa naʻa ne unu hono nima ʻi he tahi, pea naʻa ne tala ange: tau ʻi [[Fisi]]. He ko ia ko hono hingoa tenetene: '''Fāfākongatahi'''.

{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Tuita |ʻaho fakanofo= |ʻaho pongipongi= |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa=[[Kahomovailahi]] |hoko=[[Siaosi ʻUlukivaiola Tuita]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama= tangata |tamai= [[Kahomovailahi]] |faʻē= [[Fīnaukovi]] |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1825 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Makahokovalu]]|[[Lātūniua]]|[[Vuki]]|Lātūolaʻifotuika|Lātūʻotusia||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;|&nbsp;||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|Lataitokelau|Noaisiapua|Nunufaʻēkea|Faingaʻanuku|||||}} |ʻohoana1=Mateitalo Tuʻiʻāfitu |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Mekemeke]]|Tautau|Melenoa||||||}} |ʻohoana2=Siulolovao Sisi Toutaitokotaha |fānau2= {{tokoua|[[Manase Kahomovailahi]]|ʻUlukilupetea Tuita|||||||}} |}}*http://www.planet-tonga.com/forums/viewtopic.php?t=12628&postdays=0&postorder=asc&start=30
ʻI he taimi ko ia naʻe māʻulalo pē ʻa e hingoa [[:Category:Tuita|Tuita]], ʻoku ʻikai feʻunga maʻa e foha ʻo e [[:Category:Tuʻi Tonga Fefine|Tuʻi Tonga Fefine]], ko Makahokovalu. Naʻe sai ange kia te ia ko e hingoa ʻo [[:Category:Tuʻilakepa|Tuʻilakepa]]. ʻA ia, naʻe fakanofoʻi ʻa Poʻoi, hono tehina tamaitaha faʻēkehekehe, mo e hingoá. Kae ʻosi ʻene pekia, naʻe foki ʻa e hingoa ki he foha ʻo Makahokovalú.

