{{Fakaʻuhingakehe}}
*ko e kolo ʻi [[:Category:Tongatapu & takatakai|Tongatapu]] → '''[[Holonga (Tongatapu)]]'''
*ko e kolo ʻi [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]] → '''[[Holonga (Vavaʻu)]]'''

[[Image:HolongaTBU.gif|right|350px|thumb|Holonga (kolo)]]
Ko '''Holonga''' ko e kiʻi kolo ʻi he vahe hahake ʻo [[:category:Tongatapu & takatakai|Tongatapu]], tafaʻaki fangaʻuta, ʻi he Hala Tāufaʻāhau ʻi he vahaʻa ʻo [[Malapo]] mo [[ʻAlakifonua]].

ʻOku tuʻu ia ʻi he tofiʻa ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga.
{{feituʻu Tonga|21°192|175°143}}
{{potuʻi}}
{{English|more}}
[[category:Tongatapu & takatakai]]

[[Image:Foʻui.gif|right|350px|thumb|Foʻui (kolo)]]
Ko '''Foʻui''' ko e kolo ia ʻi he vahe hihifo ʻo [[:category:Tongatapu & takatakai|Tongatapu]]. ʻOku tuʻu ʻi he Hala Hihifo ʻi he vahaʻa ʻo e manga fā (ʻo e Hala Hihifo ki [[Masilamea]] mo e Hala Liku ki [[Kalaʻau]] pea mo e Hala Loto ki [[Matahau]]) mo [[Haʻavakatolo]]. Ko hono hingoa fakatenetene ko e '''Lolo paongo''' pe '''ʻUmu tangata'''.

Ko e tofiʻa ia ʻo [[:category:Vahaʻi|Vahaʻi]], pea ʻoku tuʻu hono ʻapi meʻaʻanga ʻi ai.
{{feituʻu Tonga|21°112|175°338}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Tongatapu & takatakai]]

[[Image:Haʻavakatolo.gif|right|350px|thumb|Haʻavakatolo (kolo)]]
Ko '''Haʻavakatolo''' ko e kiʻi kolo ia ʻi he vahe hihifo ʻo [[:category:Tongatapu & takatakai|Tongatapu]]. ʻOku tuʻu ʻi he Hala Hihifo ʻi he vahaʻa ʻo [[Foʻui (Tongatapu)|Foʻui]] mo [[Kolovai]]. Ko hono hingoa fakatenetene ko e '''Vai ko hiva''' pe '''[[Pua ko fanongo talanoa]]''' (ko e [[pua]] ia). Ko e tofiʻa ia ʻo [[:category:ʻAhomeʻe|ʻAhomeʻe]]. ʻOku lahi ʻa e ngaahi mātanga ʻoku ʻiloa koeʻuhi ʻenau ʻasi ʻi he ngaahi hiva ʻo [[Tuʻimala Kaho]], ko e kaumeʻa ʻo ʻAhomeʻe.

{{feituʻu Tonga|21°107|175°338}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Tongatapu & takatakai]]

[[Image:Tufuvai.gif|right|thumb|350px|Tufuvai (kolo)]]
Ko e kolo ʻo '''Tufuvai''', pe ʻoku nonou ko '''Tufu''' ʻoku tuʻu ʻi he tafaʻaki hihifo ʻo [[ʻEua]] ofi ki he matātahi. Ko e kolo ʻEua moʻoni ia, naʻe ʻikai tanupō ʻe he kakai Niua pe ʻAta.

{{feituʻu Tonga|21°363|174°966}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Tongatapu & takatakai]]

[[image:Taʻanga.gif|right|thumb|350px|Taʻanga (kolo)]]
Ko e kiʻi kolo, ofi ki [[ʻOhonua]] ʻi [[ʻEua]]. ʻOku tuʻu ʻi ai ʻa e kolisi ngoue, ko '''Hango'''.

Ko e ngaahi ʻapi kolo ʻoku tuʻu ʻi he tofiʻa ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga, kae ko e ngaahi ʻapi ʻuta ko e tofiʻa ʻo e [[:Category:Tuʻi ʻo Tonga|Tuʻi ʻo Tonga]], ʻa ia ko e tuʻi fefine.
{{feituʻu Tonga|21°340|174°950}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Tongatapu & takatakai]]

[[Image:HoumaEUA.gif|right|thumb|350px|Houma (kolo)]]
Ko e kolo ʻi he tafaʻaki tokelau ʻo [[ʻEua]], ko e ʻapi ʻo e kakai mei he motu totonu, (ʻikai hiki mei Niua pe ʻAta). ʻOku ui foki ko ''Kolotaka''.

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo e [[:Category:Tuʻi ʻo Tonga|Tuʻi ʻo Tonga]], ʻa ia ko e tuʻi fefine.
{{feituʻu Tonga|21°316|174°931}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Tongatapu & takatakai]]

{{fakaʻuhingakehe}}
*ko e kiʻi motu ʻi [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]] → '''[[Fonuafoʻou (Vavaʻu)]]'''
*ko e moʻungaafi ʻi [[:Category:Haʻapai|Haʻapai]] → '''[[Fonuafoʻou (Haʻapai)]]'''; ʻoku ui foki ko ''Falcon island''.

{{fakaʻuhingakehe}}
*ko e kiʻi motu ʻi [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]] → '''[[Fonualei (Vavaʻu)]]'''
*ko e moʻungaafi ʻi he tokelau mamaʻo ʻo Vavaʻu → '''[[Fonualei (moʻungaafi)]]'''

[[Image:Toku.gif|right|350px|thumb|Toku (motu)]]
Ko '''Tokū''' ko e motu ia, ʻi he tokelau ange kae ʻoku ofi ki [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]], ofi ki he [[tuʻahivi fakamoʻungaafi ʻo Tonga]]. Ko e moʻungaafi ia, naʻe puna ʻa e afi fakamuimui ʻi 1846, kā mahalo pē naʻe puputuʻu ia mo e [[Fonualei (moʻungaafi)]].

Naʻe kamata nofo pē ʻa e kakai ʻi Tokū ʻi he teautaʻu ʻe 17, hola ʻe kinautolu mei [[Haʻamea]] (ʻi Tongatapu) koeʻuhi naʻe kifā kinautolu ʻi he tau mo e vahe hihifo ʻi he taimi ʻo [[:Category:Tuʻi Kanokupolu|Tuʻi Kanokupolu]] ko [[Mataeletuʻapiko]]. Ko honau houʻeiki ʻo e [[:Category:Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua|Tuʻi Haʻatakalaua]]: ko Tukutukuholoipangai, mo ʻOfahehokomaikaetau, mo ha tokotaha. Ko [[Talafaiva]] ko tokotaha ʻo kinautolu (mahalo pē ko ha Talafaiva kehe ia).

Mahalo pē naʻe ʻi ai ʻa e toko-200 ʻi Tokū mo Fonualei ʻi 1846. ʻOsi ʻa e maumauʻi ʻo Fonualei, naʻe ʻunu ʻa e kakai ʻe he kau misa ki he ngaahi siasi ʻi Vavaʻu. ʻOku nofo ʻa e konga lahi taha ʻo honau hako ʻi [[Pangaimotu (Vavaʻu)]] mo [[ʻUtulei]].

ʻAlu ʻa e kakai, ʻoku lata ki ai ʻa e fanga manupuna tahi lahi ʻaupito. ʻOku ʻi ai ha lea heliaki: {{Kananga|ʻĀutō ē manu ki Tokū.}}
{{Feituʻu Tonga|18°163|174°177}}
{{potuʻi}}
*ʻO. Māhina; Reed book of Tongan proverbs; 2004; ISBN 978-0-7900-0963-6
*E.W. Gifford, Tongan Society, BPB museum bulletin 61, 1929
