{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki
|maama= tangata
|tamai= [[Vaoloa]]
|faʻē= 
|ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1600
|ʻaho pekia=
|taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}}
|taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} 
|tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|Mulikiʻeua|+++++|||||||}} 
|ʻohoana1=?
|fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Nukufalataha]]|[[Vahaʻifefeka]]|||||||}}
|}}
Ko e ʻuluaki [[:Category:Nuku|Nuku]] ia, mahalo pē teʻeki ʻeiki, kae ko e taha ʻo e ''ʻulutolu''', (vakai ki [[:Category:Haʻa Lātūhifo|Haʻa Lātūhifo]]).

