[[Image:Taʻanea.gif|right|350px|thumb|Taʻanea (kolo)]]
Ko '''Ta‘anea''' ko e kolo ʻi he tokelauhahake ʻo e motu lahi ʻo Vavaʻu, ʻoku taha ai mo [[Haʻalaufuli]].

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo [[:Category:Vahaʻi|Vahaʻi]]
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°606|173°941}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:ʻUtui.gif|right|350px|thumb|ʻUtui (kolo)]]
Ko '''ʻUtui''' ko e kolo ʻi he hahake ʻo e motu lahi ʻo Vavaʻu.

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo [[:Category:ʻAhomeʻe|ʻAhomeʻe]], kae ʻoku tuʻu foki ʻi he tafatofiʻa ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga, mo [[:Category:Tuʻiʻāfitu|Tuʻiʻāfitu]], mo [[:Category:Veikune|Veikune]], pea ʻoku ofi ko [[:Category:Tuʻipelehake|Tuʻipelehake]].
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°635|173°959}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:Tefisi.gif|right|350px|thumb|Tefisi (kolo)]]
Ko '''Tefisi''' ko e kolo ia ʻoku tuʻu ʻi he hihifo ʻo e motu lahi ʻo Vavaʻu.

Ko e konga lahi taha ko e tofiʻa ia ʻo [[:category:Luani|Luani]], ko e konga siʻi ʻi hahake ʻoku kau ki he tofiʻa ʻo [[:category:Fakafānua|Fakafānua]], pe ʻoku ui ko '''Ngaʻakau'''.
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°630|174°017}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:Taoa.gif|right|350px|thumb|Taoa (kolo)]]
Ko '''Taoa''' ko e kolo ia ʻoku tuʻu ʻi he hihifo ʻo e motu lahi ʻo Vavaʻu, ʻi ʻolunga ʻo e moʻunga, ko '''Sia ko Kafoa'''.

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo [[:category:Tupoutoʻa|Tupoutoʻa]].
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°627|173°986}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:Haʻakio.gif|right|350px|thumb|Haʻakio (kolo)]]
Ko '''Haʻakio''' ko e kiʻi kolo ia ʻoku tuʻu ʻi he vahe loto ʻo e motu lahi ʻo Vavaʻu.

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga.

Naʻe tuʻu ʻa e kolotau ʻi onoʻaho, ko Vaipoa, ʻo e ʻeiki siʻi ko Māhina ʻi Tukulalo. Taimi ʻe niʻihi naʻe ʻi ai ha kātoanga [[mafi]] lahi, ko ia ai ko e lea heliaki: {{Kananga|Vavā fakavaipoa}}
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°618|173°944}}
{{potuʻi}}
ʻO. Māhina; Reed book of Tongan proverbs; 2004; ISBN 978-0-7900-0963-6
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:Faleono.gif|right|350px|thumb|Faleono (kolo)]]
Ko '''Faleono''' ko e kiʻi kolo ia ʻoku tuʻu ʻi he vahe loto ʻo e motu lahi ʻo Vavaʻu. Kuo fakataha ia ʻi he tafaʻaki hihifo mo [[Houma (Vavaʻu)|Houma]].

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°629|173°942}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:HoumaVAV.gif|right|350px|thumb|Houma (kolo)]]
Ko '''Houma''' ko e kiʻi kolo ia ʻoku tuʻu ʻi he vahe loto ʻo e motu lahi ʻo Vavaʻu. Kuo fakataha ia ʻi he tafaʻaki hahake mo [[Faleono]].

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°628|173°944}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:Mangia.gif|right|350px|thumb|Mangia (kolo)]]
Ko '''Mangia''' ko e kiʻi kolo fakaʻofoʻofa ia ʻoku tuʻu ʻi he vahe loto ʻo e motu lahi ʻo Vavaʻu.

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga, mo e tofiʻa ʻo [[:Category:Fulivai|Fulivai]] ʻoku ofi.
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°622|173°957}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:MataikaVAV.gif|right|350px|thumb|Mataika (kolo)]]
Ko '''Mataika''' ko e kolo lahi ia ʻoku tuʻu ʻi he vahe loto ʻo e motu lahi ʻo Vavaʻu, ʻi he hala lahi mei [[Neiafu]] ki he malaʻe vakapuna.

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga, mo e tofiʻa ʻo [[:Category:Tuʻihaʻateiho|Tuʻihaʻateiho]] mo ha tofiʻa ʻo e tuʻi.
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°614|173°967}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

