In any case, editors (registered only) can give their opinions and votes on the talk (alea) page, and after a week an administrator will delete it or keep it according to the verdict.
== Quick guide to its use == Use this template on the page involved, probably on top and choose: <nowiki>{{</nowiki>Db-kole}} <font color="#060">''no further explanation needed''</font> <nowiki>{{</nowiki>Db-kole|reason}} <font color="#060">''if you want to add a particular reason''</font> {{Foki|s|Db-kole}}

