Ko '''ʻUtulei''' ko e kiʻi kolo ia tuʻu ʻi he motu ʻo [[Pangaimotu (Vavaʻu)|Pangaimotu]], fehāngaaki [[Neiafu]].

Ko e tofiʻa ʻo e kolo mo hono takatakaʻi, ko e tofiʻa ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga.
