[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:Mala.gif|right|thumb|350px|Mala (motu)]]
Ko '''Mala''' ko e kiʻi motu ia ʻi he tahi tonga ʻo Vavaʻu, ʻofi ki [[Ngaʻunoho]] mo [[Kapa]]. He ʻaho ni ʻoku manakoa ʻe he kau taki mamata, kae ʻi onoʻaho naʻe tui ʻe he taukei naʻe nofo ʻa e [[faʻahikehe]] ʻi ai.
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°688|174°023}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:Ovaka.gif|right|thumb|350px|Ovaka (motu + kolo)]]
Ko '''Ovaka''' ko e motu ia ʻo e pupunga motu fakatonga ʻo Vavaʻu. ʻOku tuʻu ʻi ai ʻa  e kolo mo hono hingoa tatau (18.742° S 174.097° W).

Ko e tofiʻa ia ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga.
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°742|174°103}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[category:Vavaʻu]]

[[Image:Ofu.gif|right|thumb|350px|Ofu (motu + kolo)]]
