Ko e tofiʻa ia ʻo e puleʻanga ʻo Tonga.

ʻI onoʻaho naʻe nofo ʻi ai ʻa e [[mānaʻia]], ko [[Lepuhā]]. Naʻe ʻikai ha fefine ʻe lava folau atu he motu taʻe sio ki he talavou ē. Ko ia ai ko e lea heliaki: {{Kananga|Hila ki Tapana}}
{{feituʻu Tonga|18°712|173°993}}
