[[Image:Pelehake.gif|right|350px|thumb|Pelehake (kolo)]]
Ko '''Pelehake''' ko e kiʻi kolo ia ʻi he loto mālie ʻo vahe hahake ʻo [[:category:Tongatapu & takatakai|Tongatapu]]. Ko e kolo foʻou ia, naʻe ʻikai hoko ha kolo kae ʻoua he tau māmani hono ua pe ofi ki ai. Ko hono hingoa tenetene ko '''Ī ʻo Lupea''' pe '''Vaomapa'''. Ko e hingoa ʻo e lautohi ʻi hihifo ko ''Lōtolu'' ia.

Ko e lotomālie ia ʻo e tofiʻa ʻo [[:Category:Tuʻipelehake|Tuʻipelehake]].
{{feituʻu Tonga|21°216|175°139}}
{{potuʻi}}
