[[Image:PangaiHPA.gif|right|350px|thumb|Pangai (kolo)]]
Ko '''Pangai''', tuʻu ʻi he motu ʻo [[Lifuka]] ko e kolomuʻa ia ʻo [[:category:Haʻapai|Haʻapai]]. Ko hono hingoa tenetene ko '''Fanga ʻi he sī''' pe '''Fanga falikipako''' pe '''Lea ʻa e tohi'''.

ʻOku tuʻu ʻa e taulanga mo e ʻōfisi kōvana, mo er pālasi ʻo e tuʻi (ko ''Toatuʻuakitau''), mo e ngaahi falakoloa mahuʻinga ʻi Pangai. ʻOku tuʻu ʻi ai ʻa e faʻitoka ʻo [[Shirley Waldemar Baker]].
{{Feituʻu Tonga|19°806|174°346}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[Category:Haʻapai]]

[[Image:Tongoleleka.gif|right|350px|thumb|Tongoleleka (kolo)]]
Ko '''Tongoleleka''' ko e tafaʻaki tonga-hihifo (ʻoku ui foki ko '''Hihifo''') ʻo e kolo lahi ʻo [[Pangai]], Haʻatoʻu mo ʻeni, ʻi he motu ʻo [[Lifuka]] ʻi [[:category:Haʻapai|Haʻapai]]. Ko hono hingoa tenetene (tatau mo Haʻapai) ko '''Vai ko Paluki'''. Mahalo pē ko Pangai ko e kolomuʻa, kā ko Tongoleleka ko e kolo ʻulungāanga taha.

Ko e tofiʻa ia ʻo [[:Category:Tuita|Tuita]], ʻoku tuʻu heni ʻa e fale fakataha ko ''Toluafe'', ofi ki ai ʻoku tuʻu ko e ''[[Maka-ko-Loupua]]''. Ko e kiʻi mamaʻo ki he tonga, naʻe tuʻu ʻa e fale mahaki ''Niuʻui'' (naʻe liʻekina ʻosi he mofuike ʻo 4 Mē 2006). ʻI he tafaʻaki hakake ʻo e koló ni ʻoku tuʻu ʻa e lusaʻanga ʻo [[Velata]].
{{Feituʻu Tonga|19°816|174°353}}
{{potuʻi}}
[[Category:Haʻapai]]

