|}}*http://epress.anu.edu.au/austronesians/origins/mobile_devices/ch12s02.html
Ko [[Fisilaumāli]] ko e pule maʻu mafai ʻo [[Pelehake]] ia, naʻe lahi hono tofiʻa, kae ko e ʻeiki māʻulalo ʻaupito. Pea naʻe fekau ʻe [[Mataelehaʻamea]], ko e [[:category:Tuʻi Kanokupolu|Tuʻi Kanokupolu]], ʻa hono ʻofefine, ko [[Fusipala]], ʻo mali mo Fisilaumāli. ʻA ia, naʻe hoko ʻa e ʻeiki lahi hono foha, ko Lekaumoana. ʻOku pehē naʻe kamata ʻa e hiki ʻo e tuʻunga ʻo e [[:category:Tuʻipelehake|Tuʻipelehake]]. Maholo pē ʻosi ko ia ko e hako ʻo [[Talafale]], ko e meʻa faʻufoʻou ia.
