[[category:Haʻapai]]

Ko e feituʻu ofi ki [[Tongoleleka]] ʻi [[Lifuka]]. ʻI 1826 naʻe tau ʻa e feingatau mahuʻinga lahi ʻe [[Siaosi Tupou I|Tāufaʻāhau]] mo [[Sanualio Laufilitonga]].
Naʻe ʻikuna ʻa Tāufaʻāhau, ko ʻene manga ʻuluaki ki he [[:Category:Tuʻi ʻo Tonga|Tuʻi ʻo Tonga]]. Ko e mole ʻo Laufilitonga naʻe tuku ʻa ʻene ʻamanaki kotoa ke hoko ko e hau lahi ʻo Tonga.
Ko e toʻa mahuʻinga ʻi he taú ni ko [[:Category:Tuʻuhetoka|Tuʻuhetoka]] ia; naʻe faʻahi mo Tāufaʻāhau. [[category:hisitōlia ʻo Tonga]] {{potuʻi}}

