{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= Mangosteen (var) |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[malpighiales]] |familia= [[CLUSIACEAE]] |tribus= [[GARCINIEAE]] |genus= Garcinia |species= myrtifolia |fakamoʻoniʻanga= A.C. Smith }} Ko e '''fetoʻumaka''', ko e fuʻu ʻakau mo haʻane toʻi namulelei.
Ko e hingoa ʻo e kāinga fakasaienisi onopooni ko e ''Clusiaceae'' ia, kae ʻoku ui foki ''Guttiferae'' pe ''Hypericaceae''. Kae māhalo pē ʻoku ui ʻa e fetoʻumaka ki he kāinga ''Sapindaceae''. ʻOku ui ʻa e fetoʻomaka ʻe Yuncker.
==Tataku== *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Ficus tinctoria.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[urticales]] |familia= [[MORACEAE]] |genus= Ficus |species= tinctoria |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Johann Reinhold Forster|J.R.Forst.]] & [[Georg Forster|G.Forst.]] |fehokotaki= }} {{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā= |faitālaulahi= 320px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[apiales]] |familia= [[PITTOSPORACEAE]] |genus= Pittosporum |species= arborescens |fakamoʻoniʻanga=W. Rich ex A. Gray }}
Ko e '''masi''' ko e ngaahi fuʻu ʻakau kehekehe. ʻOku ngāueʻaki ʻa ʻenau foʻi fua pe tenga maʻa e [[ʻaukava]]. ʻOku fefeka ʻa e foʻi fua.
==Ngaahi faʻahinga== *masikona, ''Pittosporum arborescens'' *masiʻaukava, ''Pittosporum arborescens'' *masipā, ''Ficus scabra'' pe ''Ficus tinctoria'' *masiʻata, ''Ficus scabra'' *masikoka, vakai ki he [[mālōlō]] *masikai (OLACEAE?) ** mahalo pē meimei tatau mo e [[olavai|tutuna]] mei [[ʻEua]] ** mahalo pē tatau mo e [[kōkauʻuli]] mei [[:Category:ongo Niua|ongo Niua]], kae mahalo pē ʻoku tatau ʻa e kōkauʻuli mo e [[ngatata]], ''Elattostachys falcata'' pe ''Alectryon sp'' (SAPINDACEAE)
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *mati ([[lea fakafutuna]], [[lea fakahaʻamoa]], tānaki ko e ''Ficus scabra'') *masi ([[lea fakafisi]], [[lea fakatahisi]]), ngāueʻaki maʻa fai [[ngatu]] kapau ʻoku ʻikai ʻi ai ha [[hiapo]] *masi ([[lea fakaʻuvea]]) vakai foki ki he [[ʻovava]]. *kavakava, mimi-ō-ʻIna (=mimi ʻo Hina) ([[lea fakakuki]] masikona)
==Tataku== *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=6152 ''Ficus tinctoria'' *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=6546 ''Pittosporum arborescens'' *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Flowers of the Pacific island seashore; W.A. Whistler *Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Seabeans |faitā=Starr_021203-0008_Mucuna_gigantea.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[fabales]] |familia= [[FABACEAE]] |tribus=[[MIMOSEAE]] |genus= Mucuna |species= gigantea |fehokotaki= c }} [[File:Mucuna urens MHNT.BOT.2009.16.6.jpg|thumb|''Mucuna urens'']] Ko e '''vālai''' ko e ʻakau totolo ʻi Tongá ni ia. ʻOku tatau mo e '''paʻanga ʻa e kumā''', ko e tenga ʻo e ʻakaú ni, koeʻuhi ʻoku siʻi ange ki he tenga ʻo e [[paʻanga (ʻakau)|paʻanga]].
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *tupe, fue vai ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]], ko e tenga pē; foʻi lea tatau mo e tisi [[tupe]] ʻo e [[lafo]]) *wakore ([[lea fakafisi]]) *feseka uli ([[lea fakaniuē]]) *tutae puaʻa ([[lea fakatahisi]]) *kāʻeʻe ([[lea fakahauaiʻi]])
==Tataku== *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Flowers of the Pacific island seashore; W.A. Whistler {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[sapindales]] |familia= [[RUTACEAE]] |genus=Evodia |species=hortensis }}
Ko e '''uhi''' ko e kiʻi fuʻu ʻakau mo e ngaahi kiʻi matalaʻikau siʻisiʻi mo hinehina mo manongi. Ko ''evodia'' pe ''euodia'' ʻoku haʻu mei he [[lea fakakalisi]]: namulelei. ʻOku ui foki ko e ''Evodia simplicifolia''. Ko e [[kakala vale]] ia.
==Ngaahi faʻahinga kehekehe== *uhilaukoka; faʻahinga tatau, kā ko e ngaahi lou fālahi ange *[[uhiuhi]]; meimei tatau ʻene ʻasi, kā ko e faʻahinga kehe ʻaupito vakai foki ki he [[hulufe|hulufe uhi]].
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *usi ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]]) **soʻopini, soʻopine, ''Euodia samoensis'' Christoph. *uci ([[lea fakafisi]])
==Toe meʻa kehe== ʻOku ngāueʻaki ʻa e ngaahi lou maʻa e faitoʻo ki he [[faʻahikehe]].
==Tataku== *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= Beach mulberry |faitā= P Morc D1252.JPG |faitālaulahi=300px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[gentianales]] |familia= [[RUBIACEAE]] |genus=Morinda |species=citrifolia |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''nonu''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau ia. Ko e huhu'a ʻo e foʻi fua'i nonu 'oku ngaue'aki ki he faitoʻo.
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *nono ([[lea fakatahisi]]) *noni ([[lea fakahauaiʻi]]) *nonu ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]], [[lea fakaʻuvea]], [[lea fakafutuna]]) *kura ([[lea fakafisi]]) *ura ([[lea fakalotuma]])
==Tataku== *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Multipurpose trees for agroforestry in the Pacific islands; R.R. Thaman, C.R. Elevitch, K.M. Wilkinson *Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 *D.R. Drake et al., Rain forest vegetation of ʻEua Island, New Zealand Journal of Botany '''34''', 1996 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Pemphis acidula.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[myrtales]] |familia= [[LYTHRACEAE]] |genus=Pemphis |species=acidula |fakamoʻoniʻanga= |fehokotaki= c }}
Ko e '''ngingie''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau ia, mo e ngaahi matalaʻiʻakau hinehina. ʻOku faʻa siʻisiʻi pē, kā ʻoku ne lava ʻo tupu ʻi he fuʻu ʻakau lahi. ʻOku lahi ʻene tupu ʻi he ngaahi liku ʻo Tonga.
==Ngaahi faʻahinga kehekehe== *ngingie fau *ngingie kulu *ngingie ʻuta; tupu ʻuta ange *[[kihikihitahi|ngingieʻuta]] *ngingie, ''Suriana maritima'' L. (SURIANACEAE mei he Fabales); ko e matalaʻiʻakau engeenga, ʻoku meimei tatau ʻene ʻasi kā ko e faʻahinga kehe ʻaupito ia
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *gigia ([[lea fakafisi]]) *ʻaʻie (matalaʻiʻakau hinehina, [[lea fakatahisi]]) *ʻoʻuru (matalaʻiʻakau engeenga, [[lea fakatahisi]]) *ngangie ([[lea fakakuki]]) **ngangie raupunupunu, vamuti (matalaʻiʻakau hinehina) **ngangie moe, ngangie kuru, ngangie mahakehake, lākau vili (matalaʻiʻakau engeenga) *gigie ([[lea fakaniuē]])
==Toe meʻa kehe== ʻOku tupu ʻa e ʻakaú ni ʻi he ʻoneʻone tea ʻo e matātahi pe matāliku, kae ʻikai ʻi he ʻoneʻone ʻuli ʻo e moʻungaafi (fakatātā ʻoku meimei ʻikai tupu ʻi [[Haʻamoa]]).
==Tataku== *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=6491 *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=6690 *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Flowers of the Pacific island seashore; W.A. Whistler *Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= Taro |faitā= Songe-Réunion.JPG |faitālaulahi=324 px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[alismatales]] |familia= [[ARACEAE]] |genus=Colocasia |species=esculenta |fakamoʻoniʻanga=([[Carolus Linnaeus|L]].) [[Heinrich Wilhelm Schott|Schott]] |fehokotaki= c }}
Ko e '''talo''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau ia, ʻoku mahuʻinga lahi maʻa e meʻatokoni. Ko e ongo faʻahinga mahuʻinga taha ko e talo tonga mo talo futuna. Ko e '''talo tonga''' ʻoku sai taha ʻa ʻene aka, ko e '''talo futuna''' ʻoku sai ange ʻa ʻene lou, ko e [[lū]] palau.
[[File:Xanthosoma sagittifolium.jpg|320px|thumb|left|Talo futuna]] == Ngaahi faʻahinga kehekehe == * talo tonga, ''C. esculenta'' pe ''C. antiquorum'' * talo futuna, ''Xanthosoma sagittifolium'' * talo fisi * talo haʻamoa * talo kula * talo lauʻila * talo lotuma * talo manuʻa * talo mangakoka * talo mangatefua * talo matalei * talo mumu * talo niuē * talo sikavi * talo vahemangomanga * talo vahetuʻutaha
== Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe == * talo ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]]) * taro ([[lea fakatahisi]]) * kalo ([[lea fakahauaiʻi]]) * dalo ([[lea fakafisi]])
== Tataku == * Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī * Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward * Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= Lesser yam |faitā=Dioscorea esculenta 002.JPG |faitālaulahi= 320px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[dioscoreales]] |familia= [[DIOSCOREACEAE]] |genus=Dioscorea |species=esculenta |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] }} [[Image:Củ từ luộc.JPG|thumb|left|upright=1.3|''Dioscorea esculenta'']] Ko e '''ʻufilei''' ko e foʻi ʻakau ia, ko e meʻakai, tatau mo e [[ʻufi]] kae siʻi ange.
