{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= |faitā= Garcinia pseudoguttifera.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[malpighiales]] |familia= [[CLUSIACEAE]] |tribus=[[GARCINIEAE]] |genus=Garcinia |species=pseudoguttifera |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Berthold_Carl_Seemann|Seem.]] }}
Ko e '''moʻonia''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau ia mo e matalaʻiʻakau manongi. Ko e [[kakala ʻiloa]] ia.
