{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Seaside clerodendrum |faitā=Starr_010424-0022_Clerodendrum_inerme.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[lamiales]] |familia= [[VERBENACEAE]] |genus=Clerodendrum |species=inerme |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]]) [[Joseph Gaertner|Gaertn.]] |fehokotaki= s }} Ko e '''tutuhina''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia, ʻoku tupu ʻi he matāfonua. Ko e kāinga ofi onoʻaho naʻe ''Volkameria''.
