{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[myrtales]] |familia= [[MYRTACEAE]] |genus=Decaspermum |species=fruticosa |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Michel Adanson|Adans.]] }} Ko e '''nukonuka''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia, ko e [[kakala ʻiloa]].
