{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Manioc, Cassava |faitā=Iwata kenichi cassava.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[malpighiales]] |familia= [[EUPHORBIACEAE]] |tribus = [[Manihoteae]] |genus=Manihot |species=esculenta |fakamoʻoniʻanga= Crantz |fehokotaki= c }}
