{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= Creeping clubmos |faitā=Starr_020925-0091_Lycopodiella_cernua.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau tengaefuefu]] |classis= [[lycopodiopsida]] |ordo= [[lycopodiales]] |familia= [[LYCOPODIACEAE]] |genus=Lycopodium |species=cernuum |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] }} Ko e '''ikuʻi-kulī''' pe '''hikuʻi-pusi''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. ʻOku ne fakafanau ngāueʻaki he [[tengaefuefu]]. Ko hono ''vahe'', ko e [[ʻakau tengaefuefu]], mahalo pē ʻoku ʻikai ko e ''pteridophyta'' kā ko e ''lycopodiophyta''. ʻOku lotokehekehe ʻa e kau saienisi ki ai. Tatau mo e hingoa, ʻoku ui foki ko e ''Lycopodiella cernua'', ''Palhinhaea cernua'' pe ''Lepidotis cernua''.
