{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Welwitschia mirabilis(2).jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio='''ʻakau sukau''' |genus= |species= }} Ko e '''ʻakau sukau''' (''gnetophyta'') ʻi he [[saienisi ʻo e ʻakau]] ko e taha pē ʻo e '''vahe''' ʻo e ngaahi meʻamoʻui ʻe 5 ʻi he ʻuluʻivahe ko e [[ʻakau tengaʻiʻakau]] (''spermatophytes''). ʻOku ne kau ki he pupunga ʻo e [[tengaʻiʻakau telefua]] (''gymnospermae''), tatau mo e * [[ponga paame]] (''cycadophyta'') * [[ʻakau fuasiliva]] (''ginkgophyta'') * [[ʻakau paini]] (''pinophyta'') Ko e vahe fika hono 5 ko e [[ʻakau matala]] (''magnoliophyta'') ia, ko e taha pē ia ʻi he pupunga ʻo e [[tengaʻiʻakau ʻufiʻufi]] (''angiospermae'').
ʻOku siʻi pē ʻa e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻi he vahe ʻo e ʻakau sukau, kā ʻoku ʻi ai ha ʻakau fakatāfuʻua, fakatātā ko e ''[[Welwitschia mirabilis]]'' ʻi [[ʻAfelika]] (vakai ki he faitā).
ʻOku ʻikai tupu ʻi Tongá ni ʻa e ngaahi ʻakau sukau, kā ʻoku tupu ʻa e faʻahinga ʻe taha pē ʻi [[Fisi]], ko e [[sukau]]. {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Podocarpus macrophyllus Leaves 2700px.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau paini]] |classis= [[pinopsida]] |ordo= [[pinales]] |familia= [[PODOCARPACEAE]] |genus=Podocarpus |subgenus foliolatus |species=pallidus |fakamoʻoniʻanga= N.E. Gray }} Ko e '''uhiuhi''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia, mahalo pē tatau ʻene ʻasi mo e [[uhi]], kā ʻoku kau ki he [[ʻakau paini]], ʻoku ʻikai ʻi ai hano matalaʻiʻakau. ʻOku taha ʻana ia maʻa Tongá ni.
Ko e faitā ko e ''Podocarpus macrophyllus'' ia, kā ʻoku tatau ʻene louʻakau.
