{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Widgeongrass |faitā=Ruppia maritima.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |subclassis= [[alismatidae]] |ordo= [[najadales]] |familia= [[RUPPIACEAE]] |genus=Ruppia |species=maritima |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] |fehokotaki= c }} Ko e '''limuvai''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. ʻOku tatau ʻene ʻasi mo e ngaahi [[mohuku]], ka tupu ʻi he vai, vai melie pe tahi. ʻOku kehe ʻaupito mei he [[limutahi]], ʻoku tupu ʻi he tahi pe ia foki, ʻi he maka fefeka. Kā ko e limuvai, ʻoku ʻi ai hono aka, ʻoku tupu pē ʻi he ʻoneʻone molu, ofi ke he fukahi tahi, ʻi he maama ʻo e laʻā. He onoʻaho naʻa ne fakafaʻahingaʻi ʻi he kāinga ʻo e Potamogetonaceae.
==Ngaahi faʻahinga mohuku-tahi kehekehe ʻi Tongá ni== *''Syringodium isoetifolium'' *''Diplanthera uninervis'' *''Halophila ovalis'' (Hydrocharitaceae)
==Tataku== *http://plants.usda.gov/java/profile?symbol=RUMA5 *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

'''Protists''' (''first living'') are in [[saienisi ʻo e moʻui|biology]] one of the 4 kingdoms of multi-[[lokiʻimoʻui|celled]] based life. In some way it is a rubbish collection, containing all organisms not yet included in the plants, animals and fungi. By consequence biologists heartily disagree with each other about them, and the exact list of members changes all the time. Mostly the protists are one-celled organisms, but there are some larger multi-celled organisms, especially the [[limutahi|seaweeds]].
==The kingdom of celled living creatures== *[[meʻamoʻuimuʻa|'other' organisms]], most single cell ([[leafakalatina|Latin]]: ''protista'') *[[talingelinga|fungi]] (''fungi'') *[[monumanu|animals]] (''animalia'') *[[ʻakau|plants]] (''plantae'') Other organisms without distinct cells: [[siemu|bacteria]], [[vailasi|viruses]], and so forth.
There are many different species falling under the protists, most of them only visible under the microscope. Better known are the few largers ones, the '''algae''' and '''seaweeds'''. It is customary to distinguish 4 (or even more) algae according to their colour appearance: *green algae or seaweeds ''chlorophyta'' - belongs to the [[ʻakau|plants]] *blue algae or seaweeds ''cyanobacteria'' - belongs to the [[siemu|bacteria]] as it does not have cells *red algae or seaweeds ''rhodophyta'' - real protist *brown algae or seaweeds ''phaeophyta'' - real protist, most of the larger [[limutahi|seaweeds]] Evidently only the red and brown algae are belonging to the kingdom of the protists. Yet from time to time biologists group them together is a new kingdom (independent or not), the ''chromalveolata'' or ''chromista'' (coloured algae), and sometimes they do not. {{foki||Meʻamoʻuimuʻa}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Jednoliścienne-budowa nasienia.svg |faitālaulahi= 200px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio=[[ʻakau matala]] |classis='''lautengaʻitaha''' |genus= |species= }} Ko e '''lautengaʻitaha''' ko e ''haʻa'' ʻe taha ʻo e vahe ko e [[ʻakau matala]]. ʻOku ui foki ko e ''monocotyledones'' pe ''liliopsida'', neongo ʻoku ʻi ai ʻa e saienisi ʻoku pehē ʻoku ʻikai tatau tonu kinaua.
Ko e [[lautengaʻiua]] ko e haʻa ʻe taha.
Ko e ʻata ki mataʻu: ko e tenga ʻo e lautengaʻitaha, a=kili, b=meʻakai lototenga, c=lautenga, d=ʻakau kei ʻi he tenga. {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Budowa nasienia-dwuliscienne.png |faitālaulahi= 200px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio=[[ʻakau matala]] |classis='''lautengaʻiua''' |genus= |species= }} [[Image:Starr_031108-2065_Sophora_tomentosa.jpg|thumb|left|Ko e [[lata]], ko e ʻakau lautengaʻiua]] Ko e '''lautengaʻiua''' ko e ''haʻa'' ʻe taha ʻo e ''vahe'' ko e [[ʻakau matala]]. ʻOku ui foki ko e ''dicotyledones'' pe ''magnoliopsida'', neongo ʻoku ʻi ai ʻa e saienisi ʻoku pehē ʻoku ʻikai tatau tonu kinaua.
Ko e [[lautengaʻitaha]] ko e haʻa ʻe taha.
ʻAta ki mataʻu: ko e tenga ʻo e lautengaʻiua, a=kili, b=meʻakai lototenga, c=lautenga, d=ʻakau kei ʻi he tenga. {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= |faitā= |faitālaulahi= 320px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[gentianales]] |familia= [[APOCYNACEAE]] |genus=Ochrosia |species=oppositifolia |fakamoʻoniʻanga= (Lam.) K. Schum. |fehokotaki= s }} Ko e '''fao''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia. ʻOku tatau mo e ''Neisosperma oppositifolia'' pe ''Neisosperma oppositifolium'' pe ''Ochrosia parviflora''.
