{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= |faitā= |faitālaulahi= 320px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[ericales]] |familia= [[SAPOTACEAE]] |genus=Planchonella |species=costata |fakamoʻoniʻanga= (Endl.) Pierre }} Ko e '''kalaka''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia. Mahalo pē ʻoku tatau mo e ''Planchonella garberi'' pea mo e ''Planchonella grayana''. ʻOku ui foki ko e '''ahikaulolo''' pe '''kakalaʻuli''' (kā vakai ki he [[kakalaʻuli]] ʻoku lahi).
