{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Japanese honeysuckle |faitā=Lonicera Japonica (polynesia).jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[dipsacales]] |familia= [[CAPRIFOLIACEAE]] |genus=Lonicera |species=japonica |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carl Peter Thunberg|Thunb.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''pua fisi''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. Ko e ʻakau foʻou ia, ʻomi mei muli, ko [[Siapani]] mo e [[ʻEsia]] hahake, pea naʻa ne folau ki [[Fisi]] pea ki Tongá ni. ʻOku kehe mo e [[pua]].
