{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Angel's trumpet |faitā=Brugmansia candida flowers.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[solanales]] |familia= [[SOLANACEAE]] |genus=Brugmansia |species=arborea |fakamoʻoniʻanga=[[Lagerheim.]] }} Ko e '''talupite ʻangelo '''(hingoa taʻefakalakanga) ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia. Mahalo pē ʻoku tatau mo e ''Brugmansia candida'' pe ''Brugmansia suaveolens''.
