{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Sandbur |faitā=Cenchrus echinatus closeup.jpg |faitālaulahi=290px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[poales]] |familia= [[mohuku]] |genus=Cenchrus |species=echinatus |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] }} Ko e '''hefa''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia mo e ngaahi tenga talatala. ʻOku kapusi fakatuotuai ʻa e hefa tuʻufonua (''C. calyculatus'') ʻe he hefa muli (''C. echinatus'') ==Ngaahi faʻahinga kehekehe== *hefa, hefa tuʻufonua, ''C. calyculatus'', [polynesian sandbur]; siʻi ange ʻa e ʻakau mo kiʻi molū ange ʻa e talatala ʻo e tenga *hefa, hefa muli, ''C. echinatus'', [sandbur]; lahi ange ʻa e ʻakau mo talatala masila ʻa e tenga
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *mosie vihilango, motie vihilago ([[lea fakaniuē]]) *pipiri, piripiri ([[lea fakatahisi]]) *mauʻu kukū, ʻumeʻalu ([[lea fakahauaiʻi]]) *tuitui, vao papalagi, vao tuitui, sefa ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]]) *pārango, piripiri ([[lea fakakuki]]) *se bulabula ([[lea fakafisi]])
==Tataku== *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=5904 *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Flowers of the Pacific island seashore; W.A. Whistler; ISBN 978-0-8248-1528-8 *Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

The '''smothering vine''' (unofficial name) is an introduced vine from India of the [[kiukamipā|cucumber]] family. Its fruits (unripe green or ripe bright red) can be eaten, as can anything else of the plant. It is a very aggressive plant, quickly smothering any other plant it is growing on, covering electricity poles, and so forth.
In Tonga it is usually called ''a vine'', as the plant is too new to have a local name. The English name is Scarlet gourd or Ivy gourd.
It is wildly spreaded now on [[:Category:Tongatapu & takatakai|Tongatapu]], but has not yet reached to [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]]. {{Foki||Vaine fakafulutāmakiaʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Crape ginger |faitā=Costus speciosus.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[zingiberales]] |familia= [[COSTACEAE]] |genus=Costus |species=speciosus |fakamoʻoniʻanga= (J.Konig) Sm. }} Ko e '''tēvunga muli''' (hingoa taʻefakalakanga) ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. ʻOku ʻomi mei [[ʻĒsia]] tongahahke mo [[Mikolonisia]], ko ia ai ʻoku ʻikai hano hinga fakatonga, kā ʻene ʻasi ʻoku meimei tatau mo e [[tēvunga]]. Ko hono matalaʻiʻakau ʻoku fuʻu lahi ange.
==Ngaahi faʻahinga kehekehe== *tevunga/teuila muli; koʻeni *tēvunga/teuila kula = [[tēvunga]] *tevunga/teuila tea = [[teuila]]
