{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Golden dewdrop |faitā=Duranta repens.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[lamiales]] |familia= [[VERBENACEAE]] |genus=Duranta |species=erecta |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''mavaetangi''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia, mo kiʻi matalaʻiʻakau violeti pea mo e foʻi fua lanukoula. ʻOku ui foki ko e ''D. repens'', ko e ʻakau ʻomi mei [[Mekisikō]] mo [[Kalipea]].
ʻOku ui ʻe Yunker ko e ''ʻolive'', kā ʻoku pau ko e hala ia. Ko e [[ʻolive]] fakatonga ko e ''Murraya paniculata'' ia.
