{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Crabclaw heliconia, Parrotbeak heliconia |faitā=Heliconia-psittacorum-Réunion.jpg |faitālaulahi= 250px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[zingiberales]] |familia= [[HELIOCONIACEAE]] |genus=Heliconia |species=psittacorum |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] |fehokotaki= c }} [[Image:Heliconia rostrata1.jpg|thumb|left|250px|''Heliconia rostrata'']] [[Image:Heliconia collinsiana var. collinsiana.jpg|thumb|left|250px|''Heliconia collinsiana'' var. ''collinsiana'']] [[File:Starr 070906-8370 Heliconia stricta.jpg|thumb|250px|right]] Ko e '''vaʻepaka''' pe '''ngutukakā''' pe '''helikonia''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. Ko e ʻakau ʻomi mei [[ʻAmelika]]-loto ia. Ko e ''H. psittacorum'' ʻoku faʻafai ʻi he ngaahi ngoue kakala ʻi Tongá ni, neongo ʻoku tupu ʻi ai foki ko e ''H. caribaea'' pea mo e ''H. stricta'' pea mo e ''H. rostrata'' pea mo e ''H. collinsiana'' var. ''collinsiana'' (manu ʻo e palataisi kulokula ?).
