{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= |faitā= |faitālaulahi= 320px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[gentianales]] |familia= [[RUBIACEAE]] |genus=Neonauclea |species=forsteri |fakamoʻoniʻanga= (Seem.) Merrill }} Ko e '''afa''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia, tupu ʻi he vao ʻo [[ʻEua]] pē. Ko e ʻuhinga tatau ko e ''Nauclea forsteri'' Seem. ʻOku ʻikai ʻoatu ʻa e hingoa fakatonga ʻi he tohi ʻo Yuncker, neongo ʻoku ʻi ai ʻa e hingoa tatau ʻi [[ʻUvea]] mo [[Futuna]] foki.
