{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[ericales]] |familia= [[SAPOTACEAE]] |genus=Manilkara |species=dissecta |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] }} Ko e '''ngesi''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia. ʻOku ne tātātaha ʻi Tongá ni. Ko hono ʻakau, ʻoku fefeka mo e tolonga, ko e ʻakau lelei taha maʻa e faʻu [[lali]].
==Ngaahi faʻahinga kehekehe== *sapotila (fuʻu ʻakau mo e foʻi ʻakau), ''Manilkara zapota'', [Sapodilla]; kāinga tatau
==Tataku== *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[sapindales]] |familia= [[SAPINDACEAE]] |genus=Elattostachys |species=falcata |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Seemann|Seem.]] Radlkofer }} Ko e '''ngatata''' pe '''ngatata kula''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahisiʻi ia. ʻOku ui ko e '''kōkauʻuli''' ʻi he [[:Category:ongo Niua|ongo Niua]]. Ko e ʻakau mahuʻinga maʻa e tufunga.
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *taputoʻi ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]])
