{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Butterfly pea |faitā=Clitoria ternatea.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[fabales]] |familia= [[FABACEAE]] |tribus= [[phaseoleae]] |genus=Clitoria |species=ternatea |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''paipa''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. ko e ʻakau faitoʻo.
