{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Mauritius hemp, Green aloe |faitā=Starr_041120-0950_Furcraea_foetida.jpg |faitālaulahi= 240px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[liliales]] |familia= [[AGAVACEAE]] |genus=Furcraea |species=foetida |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]]) [[Adrian Hardy Haworth|Haw.]], ''Furcraea gigantea'' |fehokotaki= c }} Ko e '''faumalila''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. ʻOku faʻu ʻa e maea mei ai, tatau mo e [[fau]]. ʻOku ui foki ʻa e ʻakau ko e ''Furcraea gigantea'' pe ''Agave gigantea'', pea ʻoku ne haʻu mei he kāinga, ʻoku haʻu mei ai ʻa e faʻahinga maea ʻe taha, ʻoku ui ko e ''sisal'' ʻi he [[lea fakapilitānia]].
