{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Fire spike, Cardinal's guard flower |faitā=Odontonema tubaeforme.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[lamiales]] |familia= [[ACANTHACEAE]] |tribus= ruellieae |genus=Odontonema |species=tubaeforme |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Antonio Bertoloni|Bertol.]]) [[Carl Ernst Otto Kuntze|Kuntze]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''totoe''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. Naʻe ʻomi ki Tongá ni taʻefuloa, kae ʻoku manakoa ʻi he ngoue. Ko e hingoa totoe (hingoa taʻefakalakanga), ʻoku haʻu ia mei he lea fakahaʻamoa, neongo ʻoku ʻikai pau ʻi hē. Ko hono ngaaho ʻuhingi tatau: ''Odontonema callistachyum'', ''Odontonema strictum''. Ko e ''Odontonema cuspidatum'' ko e faʻahinga kehe pe tatau ?
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *totoe ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]])
==Tataku== *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=6450 *http://www.hear.org/pier/species/odontonema_tubaeforme.htm {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Gray91.png |faitālaulahi=200px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |phylum='''monumanu filo siliva''' |genus= |species= }} Ko e '''monumanu filo siliva''' ([[lea fakalatina]] (lea fakasaienisi): ''chordata'') ko e vahe (''phylum'') ia ʻo e ngaahi monumanu kotoa ʻoku ʻi ai ʻa hanau filo siliva, pea mo hanau huituʻa kā ʻikai ko e kātoa.
ʻOku vahevaheʻi ʻa e vahé ni aʻu ki he māʻolunga ʻo e ngaahi '''haʻa''' (''classes'') ʻoku pehē: * vahe siʻi '''monumanu pulupulu''' (''urochordata'') ko honau filo siliva pē; ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 3000 tupu * vahe siʻi: '''monumnau taʻeʻulupoko''' (''cephalochordata'') ʻoku ʻi ai ʻa hanau huituʻa siʻi, hanau ngutu pea ʻikai hanau ʻulu; ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 30 tupu * vahe siʻi: '''monumanu huituʻa''' (''vertebrata'') ko e huituʻa moʻoni moʻonautolu; ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 57739 ** vahe siʻi ange: '''monumanu taʻekaungao''' (''agnatha'') ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 100 tupu ** vahe siʻi ange: '''monumanu kaungao''' (''gnathostomata'') *** haʻa: '''[[ika niuniu]]''' (''chondrichthyes'') ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 300 tupu; ʻanga *** haʻa lahi: '''ika huihui''' (''osteichthyes'') ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 30000 tupu; ika **** haʻa: '''[[ika kaponga tala]]''' (''actinopterygii'') ko e lahi tahi ʻo e ngaahi ika, faʻahinga ʻe 30000 **** haʻa: '''[[ika kaponga uoua]]''' (''sarcopterygii'') ko e ika mo e kaponga malohi, ngāueʻaki he vaʻe, pea ʻoku ʻi ai honau laumea mo e maʻamaʻa foki, faʻahinga ʻe 100 pē *** haʻa lahi: '''monumanu veʻefā''' (''tetrapoda'') ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 18000 tupu **** haʻa: '''[[monumanu nofo ʻuta mo vai]]''' (''amphibia'') ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 6000 tupu; poto **** haʻa: '''[[monumanu ngaolo pe totolo]]''' (''sauropsida'') ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 8225 tupu; fonu **** haʻa: '''[[manupuna]]''' (''aves'') ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 1 mano tupu **** haʻa: '''[[monumanu fakahuhu]]''' (''mammalia'') ko e ngaahi faʻahinga ʻe 5800 tupu mo e ha ngaahi vahe pe haʻa kehe ʻoku siʻisiʻi ʻenau mahuʻinga.
ʻOku toe ʻa e ngaahi vahevahe kehe, ʻoku manakoa ʻe he kau saienisi ʻe taha. Fakatātā: ko e monumanu veʻefā ko e tama ʻo e ika koponga uoua pea ʻikai ha tamai, koeʻuhi naʻe tupu ʻa e fanga monumanu veʻefā ʻi he [[liliu fakalakalaka ʻo e ngaahi faʻahinga]] mei he ika koponga uoua. {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Gogonasus BW.jpg |faitālaulahi=350px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |phylum=[[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis='''Ika kaponga uoua''' |genus= |species= }} Ko e ngaahi '''ika kaponga uoua''' (''sarcopterygii'') ko e pupunga ʻo e ika mo e honau kaponga malohi, meimei tatau mo e ngaahi vaʻe.
ʻOku siʻisiʻi pē ʻa e ngaahi ika kaponga uoua, ko e ika ʻiloa taha mahalo pē ko e ''[[Coelacanth]]''. Ko e lahi taha ʻo e haʻa lahi, ko e ngaahi '''ika huihui''' (''osteichthyes'') ko e ngaahi [[ika kaponga tala]] ia.
Kā ʻi he [[liliu fakalakalaka ʻo e ngaahi faʻahinga]] ko e ngaahi ika ʻeni ko e foʻi kupu mahuʻinga taha ia ʻi he vahaʻa ʻo e ngaahi meʻamoʻui ʻi tahi (ika) mo e ngaahi meʻamoʻui ʻi fonua (monumanu veʻefā). Naʻe hoko ia taʻu ʻe 400 miliona kuo hili pe ofi ki ai. Fakatātā ko e faʻahinga ʻo e ''Gogonasus andrewsae'' (ʻasi ʻi he faitā). {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Early Shark.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |phylum=[[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis='''ika niuniu''' |genus= |species= }} ʻOku ʻi ai ha ongo haʻa (''classis'') ʻi he vahe siʻi ʻo e ngaahi '''monumanu kaungao''' pe '''ika kaungao''', (''gnathostomata''): *'''ika huihui''' (''osteichthyes''), ko honau ʻū hui, ko e hui moʻoni; ʻoku vaheʻi ʻi ua: **'''[[ika kaponga tala]]''' (''actinopterygii'') **'''[[ika kaponga uoua]]''' (''sarcopterygii'') *'''ika niuniu''' (''chondrichthyes''), ko honau ʻū hui, ʻoku ʻikai faʻu he hui, kā ko e niuniu pe.
Ko e ngaahi ika kau ki ai: *[[ʻanga]] **[[ʻangatea]] **[[fakahikuʻulua]] **[[ʻangaʻangamofai]] **[[matai]] **[[lātea]] **[[tenifa]] **[[ʻaho]] **[[ʻalava]] **[[kapakauhingano]] **[[neiufi]] *[[fai]] **[[faikili]] **[[faimanu]] **[[faipala]] **[[faitalaʻingatae]] **[[faitoho]]
{{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Bluegum |faitā=Starr_031002-0027_Eucalyptus_globulus.jpg |faitālaulahi= 240px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[myrtales]] |familia= [[MYRTACEAE]] |genus=Eucalyptus |species=globulus |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Jacques-Julien Houtou de La Billardière|Labill.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''pulukamu''' (blue gum) ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia, ʻomi mei [[ʻAositēlia]]. ʻOku lahi ʻaupito ʻa e ngaahi faʻahinga, pea ʻoku ʻikai pau ko e fē faʻahinga ʻoku tupu ʻi Tongá ni. Mahalo pē ko e ''Eucalyptus citriodora'', ''E. deglupta'', ''E. saligna'', ''E. tereticornis'' ?
== Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe == * ʻūpē, purukamu ([[lea fakakuki]])
== Tataku == * Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī * Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward * Multipurpose trees for agroforestry in the Pacific islands; R.R. Thaman, C.R. Elevitch, K.M. Wilkinson * Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Buffalo, Guinea grass |faitā=Panicum maximum.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[poales]] |familia= [[mohuku]] |genus=Panicum |species=maximum |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Jacq.]] }} Ko e '''saafa''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia, ko e [[mohuku]] ia. Naʻe ʻomi ki Tongá ni mei [[ʻAfelika]], naʻe pehē ko e ngaahi tenga ʻi he kofukofu saafa ([[lea fakapilitānia]]: ''chaff''). Ko e mohuku ʻoku lava tupu mita ʻe 4 ʻi olunga, ʻoku vaoa mo e taʻefiemaʻu. Ko hono ngaahi ʻuhinga tatau: ''Megathyrsus maximus'' mo ''Urochloa maxima''.
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *vao kini ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]]) *tinikarāti, tine ([[lea fakakuki]])
==Tataku== *http://www.hear.org/pier/species/panicum_maximum.htm *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Ecuador laurel |faitā=Cordia alliodora.jpg |faitālaulahi= 320px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[lamiales]] |familia= [[BORAGINACEAE]] |genus=Cordia |species=alliodora |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Hipólito Ruiz López|Ruiz]] & [[José Antonio Pavón|Pav.]]) [[Lorenz Oken|Oken]] |fehokotaki= s }} Ko e '''kotia''' (hingoa mei he [[lea fakalatina]]) ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia, sai maʻa e tufunga. Naʻe ʻomi ki Tongá ni (ʻoku lahi ʻi ʻEua) taʻefuoloa mei [[ʻAmelika tonga]], kā ʻoku tupu he taimí ni tatau ko e vao.
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *kotia ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]])
