{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= |faitā= |faitālaulahi= 320px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[malpighiales]] |familia= [[PHYLLANTHACEAE]] |genus=Flueggea |species=flexuosa |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Johannes Müller Argoviensis|Müll. Arg.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''poumuli''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia. ʻOku moʻoni ko e ''pou mei muli'' (mei Vanuatu pe hihifo ange), ʻoku tupu pē ʻi [[Niuatoputapu]] mo [[Tafahi]], pea ʻi [[Haʻamoa]]. Sai maʻa e faʻu ngaahi pou (langa fale). ʻOku ʻikai kei ngāueʻaki hono ʻuhinga tatau: ''Securinega flexuosa'' (Müll. Arg.) Müll.Arg. pe ''Securinega samoana'' Croizat.
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *poutea ([[lea fakafutuna]]) *pou ([[lea fakalotuma]], [[lea fakafisi]]) *poumuli ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]], [[lea fakaʻuvea]]) *namamau , mamava, … ([[Vanuatu]]) *mamafua, mavua , … ([[ʻOtu motu Solomone]])
