{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Chaff flower, Devil's horsewhip |faitā=Achyranthes aspera0.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[caryophyllales]] |familia= [[AMARANTHACEAE]] |genus=Achyranthes |species=aspera |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''tamatama''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. ʻOku talatalaʻi. ʻOku ʻomi ʻi Tongá ni (mo e lahi ngaahi ʻotu motu ʻi [[Polinisia]]) mei [[ʻEsia]] tongahahake kuo fuoloa ʻaupito.
