{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Sponge cucumber |faitā=Luffa cylindrica1.jpg |faitālaulahi= 240px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[cucurbitales]] |familia= [[CUCURBITACEAE]] |genus=Luffa |species=aegyptiaca |fakamoʻoniʻanga= Mill. |fehokotaki= cs }}
[[File:Luffa aegyptiaca MHNT.BOT.2011.3.94.jpg|thumb|''Luffa aegyptiaca'']]
Ko e '''fangu ʻa kumā''' pe '''mafaʻi''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. Ko e fangu ia, sai ki he kai ʻi he taimi lanumata, pea sai he oma fufulu ʻi mui ange. ʻOku ui foki he onoʻaho ko e ''Luffa cylindrica'' var. ''insularum''.
==Ngaahi faʻahinga kehekehe== *[[fangu]] *[[hina (ʻakau)]]
