{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Reinwardt's cherry |faitā=Eugenia reinwadrtiana fruit and foliage.jpg |faitālaulahi= 320px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[myrtales]] |familia= [[MYRTACEAE]] |genus=Eugenia |species=reinwardtiana |fakamoʻoniʻanga= Blume }} [[Image:Eugenia reinwardtiana (4821230211).jpg|thumb|left|''Eugenia reinwardtiana'']] Ko e '''unuoi''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. ʻOku tātātaha ʻi Tongá ni, naʻe ʻomi mei [[ʻAositelēlia]]. ʻOku ui foki ko e ''Xylosma reinwardtiana'' (ko e hala ia?, ko e kāinga kehe); pe ko e ''Jossinia reinwardtiana'' (ʻoku ʻikai toe ngāueʻaki ʻe he taha, ʻoku kei ngāueʻaki ʻe he taha); pe ko e ''Eugenia reinwardhana'' (hala ia?); pe ''Eugenia rarifloria''. Pea naʻe ui ʻe Yuncker ko e ''Xylosma bryanii'' (SALICACEAE), mahalo pē naʻa ne fetongi ia mo e ''Xylosma orbiculatum'', ko e [[filimoto]] ?
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *nioi ([[lea fakatahisi]], [[lea fakahauaiʻi]]) *unuoi ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]]) *nīʻoi, venevene ([[lea fakakuki]])
