{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Metalleaf plant, Red ivy |faitā=Hemigraphis alternata (leaves).jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[lamiales]] |familia= [[ACANTHACEAE]] |genus=Hemigraphis |species=alternata |fakamoʻoniʻanga= (Burm.f.) T.Anderson |fehokotaki= c }} Ko e '''suipi''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia. ʻOku faingofua hoʻo toe ʻilo. Ho hono lau ʻoku lanumata pe lanufekika mo e ngingila fakamētali ʻi olunga, pea lanu fisiʻifekika ʻi lalo. Ko e ʻakau ʻomi mei [[Sava]] ([[ʻInitōnisia]]) ʻikai fuoloa, ʻa ia ʻoku ʻikai hano hingoa fakatonga. Ko e 'suipi' (hingoa taʻefakalakanga) ʻoku tupu mei [[Haʻamoa]]. ʻOku tatau mo e ''H. colorata'' pe ''Ruellia alternata'', kae ʻoku ʻikai ko e ''Strobilanthes''.
