{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Pandakaki, Bananabush |faitā=Tabernaemontana pandacaqui Blanco1.41.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[gentianales]] |familia= [[APOCYNACEAE]] |genus=Tabernaemontana |species=pandacaqui |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Jean-Baptiste Lamarck|Lam.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''teʻeteʻemanu''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia, mo e ngaahi matalaʻiʻakau hinehina, ʻoku meimei tatau mo e [[kalosipani]]. Ko hono ngaahi ʻuhinga tatau: ''Ervatamia obtusiuscula'', ''Ervatamia orientalis'', ''Tabernaemontana orientalis'', ''Ervatamia pubescens'', ''Ervatamia floribunda''. Kā, ʻoku pehē ʻe he saienisi ʻe niʻihi ʻoku kehe ʻa e faʻahinga ''orientalis'' mo e ''pandacaqui''.
