==Tataku== *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=13395 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Aloe vera |faitā=Starr_011104-0040_Aloe_vera.jpg |faitālaulahi= 240px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[asparagales]] |familia= [[ASPHODELACEAE]] |genus=Aloe |species=vera |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]]) [[Nicolaas Laurens Burman|Burm.f.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''ʻaloe''' (mei he [[lea fakapilitānia]]) ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia, ʻomi ki Tongá ni. ʻOku ne tupu ʻe he kau faʻa maʻa e paʻanga.
== Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe == * ʻāroe, ʻarovera ([[lea fakakuki]])
== Tataku == * Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Silky oak |faitā=Grevillea robusta-1.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[proteales]] |familia= [[PROTEACEAE]] |genus=Grevillea |species=robusta |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Allan Cunningham (botanist)|A.Cunn.]] ex [[Robert Brown|R.Br.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''ʻoke''' pe '''ʻoka kilika''' (ko e ua mei he [[lea fakapilitānia]]) ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia, ʻomi ki Tongá ni mei [[ʻAositelēlia]]. ʻOku manakoa ʻi he ngoue Tonga koeʻuhi hono matalaʻiʻakau.
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *haʻiku keʻokeʻo ([[lea fakahauaiʻi]])
==Tataku== *http://www.hear.org/pier/species/grevillea_robusta.htm *Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Tobacco |faitā=Tabak 9290019.JPG |faitālaulahi= 250px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[solanales]] |familia= [[SOLANACEAE]] |genus=Nicotiana |species=tabacum |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''tapaka''' (mei he [[lea fakapilitānia]]) ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia, ʻomi ki Tongá ni. Taimi ʻe niʻihi ʻoku tupu ʻe he kau faʻa maʻa ʻenau ifi.
== Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe == * tapaka ([[lea fakaniuē]]) * paka ([[lea fakahauaiʻi]]) * tapaʻa ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]]) * ʻavaʻava, avaava ([[lea fakakuki]], [[lea fakatahisi]]) * tavako ([[lea fakafisi]])
== Tataku == * Hokohoko ngaahi ʻakau; Vaʻa fekumi ngoue Vainī * Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward * Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

