{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Brazilian stink grass |faitā=Starr_030418-0047_Melinis_minutiflora.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[poales]] |familia= [[mohuku]] |genus=Melinis |species=minutiflora |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Ambroise Marie François Joseph Palisot de Beauvois|P.Beauv.]] |fehokotaki= s }} {{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Para grass |faitā=Starr_031210-0091_Urochloa_mutica.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[poales]] |familia= [[mohuku]] |genus=Urochloa |species=mutica |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Peter Forsskål|Forssk.]]) [[T.Q.Nguyen]] |fehokotaki= s }} Ko e '''puakatau''' ko e ongo faʻahinga [[mohuku]] ia, kae ko e ongo kāinga kehe. ʻOku na tātātaha. Ko e ngaahi ʻuhinga tatau ʻo e ''U. mutica'': ''Brachiaria mutica '', ''Panicum muticum'', mo e hā fua
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *mauku puakatoro, para karāti ([[lea fakakuki]]) (''U. m'')
==Tataku== *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *http://www.hear.org/pier/species/melinis_minutiflora.htm *http://www.hear.org/pier/species/urochloa_mutica.htm *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=5833 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Hairy spurge |faitā=Euphorbia hirta.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[malpighiales]] |familia= [[EUPHORBIACEAE]] |genus=Chamaesyce |species=hirta |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]]) Millsp. |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''sākisi''' (mei he ''circus'', [[lea fakapilitānia]]) ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi mo e vao ia, ʻomi ki Tongá ni. ʻOku ui foki ko e ''Euphorbia hirta'' L., ''Euphorbia pilulifera''. ʻOku ne tupu ʻi he feituʻu mafana kotoa ʻo māmani.
==Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe== *toto tāne ([[lea fakaniuē]]) *eaea, titanai, raʻau topau ([[lea fakatahisi]]) *koko kahiki ([[lea fakahauaiʻi]]) *laʻau faimoti ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]]) *totototo, totototo tītā ([[lea fakakuki]]) *eaea mata, feeimata ([[lea fakamākuise]]) *deniose, ovuku, samuqawe ([[lea fakafisi]]) *te tarai kusaie ([[lea fakakilipasi]])
==Tataku== *http://www.hear.org/pier/species/chamaesyce_hirta.htm *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=5915 *Plants of Tonga; T.G. Yuncker; BPB bulletin '''220''', Honolulu 1959 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |faitā=Cyathula prostrata leaves.jpg |faitālaulahi= 250px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[caryophyllales]] |familia= [[AMARANTHACEAE]] |genus=Cyathula |species=prostrata |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Carolus Linnaeus|L.]]) Blume }} Ko e '''tolomoʻunga''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia.
