{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Fruitsalad plant |faitā=Monstera deliciosa A.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻitaha]] |ordo= [[alismatales]] |familia= [[ARACEAE]] |genus=Monstera |species=deliciosa |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Frederik Michael Liebmann|Liebm.]] |fehokotaki= c }} Ko e '''monesitela''' (mei he [[lea fakalatina]]) ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi mo totolo ia, naʻe ʻomi ki Tongá ni ʻikai fuoloa. ʻOku fakaofo hono ngaahi lau; ʻoku makoko lahi kinautolu. ʻOku sai ke kai hono foʻi fua, kapau ʻoku moho ʻaupito, mahalo ʻosi he taʻu ʻe taha ʻo e moto. Kapau te ke feinga ke kai teʻeki moho ʻoku fifisi ʻaupito.
