{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Granny's bonnet |faitā=Angelonia salicariifolia.jpg |faitālaulahi= 240px |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[lamiales]] |familia= [[PLANTAGINACEAE]] (SCROPHULARIACEAE) |genus=Angelonia |species=salicariifolia |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Friedrich Wilhelm Heinrich Alexander Freiherr von Humboldt|Humb.]] & [[Aimé Bonpland|Bonpl.]] |fehokotaki= s }} Ko e '''ʻuluʻingeli''' (hingoa taʻefakalakanga, mei he [[lea fakakuki]]) ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia, ʻomi ki Tongá ni, tupu ʻi he ngaahi ngoue ʻe niʻihi.
