{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Mexican sunflower |faitā=Tithonia rotundifolia 'Fiesta Del Sol' Flower and Leaves 1600px.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[asterales]] |familia= [[ASTERACEAE]] |genus=Tithonia |species=rotundifolia |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Philip Miller|Mill.]]) [[Sidney Fay Blake|S.F.Blake]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''siolaʻā mekesikō''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia, ʻomi ki Tongá ni mei [[ʻAmelika]] loto ([[Mekesikō]]). ʻOku meimei tatau ʻa e ʻasi ʻa hono matala ki he [[siolaʻā]] lahi, kā ʻoku siʻisiʻi ange, mahalo pe senitimita ʻe 5 pē, mo lanu momoho, pea mo e kāinga ofi kehe.
