{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Red-vented Bulbul |faitā=Red-vented Bulbul (Pycnonotus cafer)- nominated race at Hodal I IMG 9743.jpg |faitālaulahi= 280px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[passeriformes]] |familia= [[PYCNONOTIDAE]] |genus=Pycnonotus |species=cafer |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|Linnaeus]] 1766 |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''manufoʻou''' ko e manupuna mafolalahia ʻaupito ʻi Tongá ni, ka ʻomi mei [[Fisi]]. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 20. ʻOku kulokula ʻa hono fulufuluʻi ʻusi. ʻOku ui foki ko e '''fuiva''', ka ko e [[fuiva]] moʻoni ko e manupuna kehe pea mo siʻisiʻi ʻene ʻiloa.
Ko e fanga manufoʻou ʻo [[ʻInitia]] (''P. c. bengalensis'') ʻoku ʻuliʻuli ange honau fulufulu ʻi lalo.
