{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Reef heron, Eastern reef egret |faitā=Eastern Reef Egret - dark and light morphs-trim.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[ciconiiformes]] |familia= [[ARDEIDAE]] |genus=Egretta |species=sacra |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]] 1789 |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''motuku''' (pe '''motuku lahi''', koeʻuhi ʻoku ʻi ai ha ngaahi motuku kehe) ko e manupuna tuʻufonua mo e mafolalahia ʻi Tongá ni ia. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 60. ʻOku ne nofo ofi ki he ngaahi anovai (vai melie).
ʻOku fulutui hono fulufulu ʻo manupuna ʻe taha, ʻoku hinehina ʻo e manupuna ʻe taha, pea ʻoku pulepule ʻo e motuku ʻe taha foki.
== Tataku == *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Whitefaced heron |faitā=Egretta novaehollandiae 02 gnangarra.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[ciconiiformes]] |familia= [[ARDEIDAE]] |genus=Egretta |species=novaehollandiae |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[John Latham|Latham]] 1790 |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''motuku''' (pe '''motuku foʻou''', koeʻuhi ʻoku ʻi ai ha ngaahi motuku kehe) naʻe aʻu ki Tongatapu mei [[Nuʻusila]] ʻi 1988. Ko e manupuna tuʻufonua ʻi Tongá ni he taimí ni. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 65. ʻOku ne nofo ofi ki he ngaahi anovai (vai melie).
Naʻe ui foki ko e ''Ardea novaehollandiae''.
== Tataku == * D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Mangrove heron, Striated heron |faitā=Butorides (striatus) virescens - Lee Karney FWS.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[ciconiiformes]] |familia= [[ARDEIDAE]] |genus=Butorides |species=striata |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|Linnaeus]] 1758 |fehokotaki= cs }} [[File:Héron à dos vert MHNT.jpg|thumb|''Butorides striatus'']]
Ko e '''motuku''' (pe '''motuku siʻi''', koeʻuhi ʻoku ʻi ai ha ngaahi motuku kehe) ko e manupuna ʻauhē ʻi Tongá ni ia. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 35. ʻOku ne nofo ofi ki he ngaahi anovai (vai melie).
