{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Wandering tattler |faitā=WanderingTattler23.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[charadriiformes]] |familia= [[kiu|SCOLOPACIDAE]] |genus=Tringa |species=incana |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1789) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''kiu''' (pe '''kiu tea''' ki he fakaʻehiʻehi maveuveu) ko e manupuna ʻoku ʻasi fakataʻu ʻi Tonga kotoa mei he Sēpitema ki ʻEpeleli. ʻI he taimi ʻoku toe, ko e taimi fakafānau ai, ʻoku nau nofo ofi ki he kiʻi vaitafe ʻi [[Kanata]] pe [[ʻAlasika]].
Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 27. Ko hono ʻuhinga onopooni ʻe taha: ko e ''Heteroscelus incanus''. ʻI he [[lea fakahauaiʻi]]: ko e ''ulili''.
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Sanderling |faitā=Calidris-alba-001.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[charadriiformes]] |familia= [[kiu|SCOLOPACIDAE]] |genus=Calidris |species=alba |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Peter Simon Pallas|Pallas]], 1764 |fehokotaki= cs }} [[File:Arcticsanderling.jpg|left|300px|thumb|ko e feituʻu fakafānau ʻo e kiú ni ʻi he ʻāketika]] Ko e '''kiu''' (pe '''kiu vave''' ki he fakaʻehiʻehi maveuveu) ko e manupuna ʻoku ʻasi fakataʻu ʻi he Sēpitema ki ʻEpeleli, kā ʻoku hāhāmolofia. Taimi ʻ e niʻhi ʻoku ne fotu ʻi he ngaahi matātahi ʻoneʻone, ʻoku ne femoʻuekina taimi kotoa pē. Ko e kiu siʻisʻi ange ʻo e ngaahi kiu kotoa. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 20.
ʻI he taimi ʻoku nau fakafānau ai, ʻoku nau nofo ofi ki he tokelau mamaʻo ʻo e [[ʻĀketika]]. ʻOku lahi ange ʻa e ʻuliʻuli ʻo honau fulufulu ʻi he taimi ē, kā ʻoku meimei hinehina lolotonga ʻenau nofo ʻi Tongá ni.
== Tataku == * D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Ruddy turnstone |faitā=Arenaria interpres (habitus).jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[charadriiformes]] |familia= [[kiu|SCOLOPACIDAE]] |genus=Arenaria |species=interpres |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Carolus Linnaeus|Linnaeus]], 1758) |fehokotaki= cs }} [[Image:Arenaria interpres SK.jpg|left|320px|thumb|ko e kiu ʻi he taimi taʻefakafānau]] [[File:Arenaria interpres MHNT.jpg|thumb|''Arenaria interpres'' ]]
Ko e '''kiu''' (pe '''kiu vaʻesiʻi''' ki he fakaʻehiʻehi maveuveu) ko e manupuna ʻoku ʻasi fakataʻu ʻi he Sēpitema ki ʻEpeleli, kā ʻoku lahi. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 23. ʻOku nounou hono vaʻe lāunga ha ngaahi kiu kehe. ʻOku hoihoifua ʻa hono fulufulu ʻi he taimi fakafānau, kā ʻoku nofo ia ʻi he taimi ko ia ʻi he tokelau mamaʻo ʻo e [[ʻāketika]]. ʻOku melomelo ange ʻa e fulufulu ʻi he taimi taʻefakafānau.
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Bristlethighed curlew |faitā=Bristle-thighed Curlew.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[charadriiformes]] |familia= [[kiu|SCOLOPACIDAE]] |genus=Numenius |species=tahitiensis |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1789) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''kiu foaʻunga''' ko e manupuna ʻoku ʻasi fakataʻu ʻi he Sēpitema ki ʻEpeleli, kā ʻoku siʻisiʻi pē ʻi he ngaahi motu ʻikai nofoʻi. ʻOku toe ʻa e ngaahi manuopuna siʻisiʻi pē ʻi māmani, mahalo pe ko e 7000 pē. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 42, ko e kiu lahi taha ia. ʻOku ʻilonga ʻene tangi.
Ko ʻene feituʻu fakafānau ai ʻoku mamaʻo ʻi he tokelau, ko e ngaahi toafa momoko ʻo e [[Vaitafe Yukon]] mo e [[Muitolotolo Seward]] ʻi [[Kanata]].
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Wattled honeyeater |faitā=Wattled Honeyeater (Foulehaio carunculata).jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[passeriformes]] |familia= [[MELIPHAGIDAE]] |genus=Foulehaio |species=carunculata |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1788) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''fuleheu''' ko e manupuna tuʻufonua ʻi Tongá ni, ʻoku faʻa ʻene ʻasi ʻi he ngaahi matalaʻiʻakau kumi ʻenau huhuʻa melie .
Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 19.
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Bluecrowned lory |faitā=Vini australis.JPG |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[psittaciformes]] |familia= [[PSITTACIDAE]] |genus=Vini |species=australis |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1788) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''henga''' ko e manupuna tuʻufonua ʻi Tongá ni, kā ʻoku ʻikai ʻi he ngaahi motu ʻoku ʻi ai haʻanau [[kumā ʻato]]. ʻOku ʻilo ʻi [[Late]], [[Niuafoʻou]], [[Tofua]] mo [[ʻEueiki]]. ʻOku ʻilo foki ʻi [[Fafā]], [[Haʻafeva]], [[Fotuhaʻa]], [[Tungua]], [[ʻUiha]], [[Tafahi]], pea mo e [[Haʻamoa]] mo e ʻotu motu [[Lau]].
Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 19. ʻOku ui ko e '''segavao''' ʻi [[Haʻamoa]].
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Redshining parrot |faitā=Red Shining-parrot.jpg |faitālaulahi=220px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[psittaciformes]] |familia= [[PSITTACIDAE]] |genus=Prosopeia |species=tabuensis |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1788) |fehokotaki= cs }} [[File:Tonga 1998 T$1.jpg|left|thumb|250px]] Ko e '''kōkī''' pe '''kakā''' ko e manupuna mei [[Fisi]] ia, ([[Vanua Levu]] mo [[Taveuni]]), kā naʻe ʻomi ʻi Tongá ni ʻoku fuoloa. Ko e manupuna moʻoni ia ʻo [[ʻEua]], ka ʻoku ʻomi foki ki [[Late]] ʻi 1994, pea ki he vao ʻo [[Toloa (Tongatapu)|Toloa]] ʻi Tongatapu.
Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 45.
== Tataku == *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Tongan whistler |faitā= |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[passeriformes]] |familia= [[PACHYCEPHALIDAE]] |genus=Pachycephala |species=jacquinoti |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Charles Lucien Bonaparte|Bonaparte]], 1850 |fehokotaki= s }} Ko e '''hengehenga''' ko e manupuna ia, ʻilo ʻi Tongá ni pē. Ka ʻoku ne nofo pē ʻi [[Late]] pea mo e ngaahi motu siʻisiʻi pē ʻi [[:category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]].
