{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=European starling |faitā=Sturnus vulgaris m.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[passeriformes]] |familia= [[STURNIDAE]] |genus=Sturnus |species=vulgaris |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Linnaeus]], 1758 |fehokotaki= cs }} [[File:Sturnus vulgaris MHNT.ZOO.2010.11.215.Courtalain28.jpg|thumb|'' Sturnus vulgaris'']]
Ko e '''misi pālangi''' ko e manupuna ʻomi mei muli, mei [[Nuʻusila]] ia, ʻosi ʻene ʻomi ʻi hē ʻi 1862 mei [[ʻEulope]]. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 20. ʻOku fakangatangata pē ki [[ʻEua]] mo [[:Category:Tongatapu & takatakai|Tongatapu]]. Ko hono fulufulu ʻoku ʻuliʻuli, tatau mo ha misi (misinale) mo hono vala malala. Neongo ʻoku ʻi ai foki ha [[misi]] tuʻufonua. Ko e fulufulu mo e kiʻi tapa engeenga ka ʻoku ngata pē ki he taimi ʻoku foʻou ʻa e fulufulu. ʻOku melomelo ʻa e fulufulu ki he fanga manupuna ʻeni ʻoku mui.
== Tataku == * D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Barn owl |faitā=Schleiereule.jpg |faitālaulahi=240px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[strigiformes]] |familia= [[TYTONIDAE]] |genus=Tyto |species=alba |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Giovanni Antonio Scopoli|Scopoli]], [[1769]]) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''lulu''' ko e manupuna tuʻufonua mo mafolalahia ʻi Tongá ni, pea foki ʻi he ngaahi konga lahi ʻo māmani. Neongo ia ʻoku siʻisiʻi pē hono ʻilo ʻe he kakai koeʻuhi ʻoku lele ia lolotonga he pō ʻi heʻene siu ki he fanga kumā. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 35.
