{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Buff-banded rail |faitā=Buff-banded Rail Fafa Island.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[gruiformes]] |familia= [[RALLIDAE]] |genus=Gallirallus |species=philippensis |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1789) |fehokotaki= cs }} [[File:Gallirallus philippensis MHNT.ZOO.2010.11.69.7.jpg|thumb| ''Gallirallus philippensis'']] Ko e '''veka''' ko e manupuna tuʻufonua i Tongá ni pe mo mafolalahia. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 25. ʻOku ne lata ʻi he vao fihi. ʻOku ui '''Moho-pereru''' ʻi he [[lea fakamauli]].
ʻOku kau ki he kāinga tatau mo e [[moho (manupuna)|moho]], ko e manupuna siʻi ange mo tātātaha.
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |hingoa=Pekepeka |name=Pacific swallow |faitā= HirundoTahiticaGould.jpg |faitālaulahi=280px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[passeriformes]] |familia= [[HIRUNDINIDAE]] |genus=Hirundo |species=tahitica |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1789 |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''pekepeka''' ko e manupuna tuʻufonua ʻi Tongá ni, ka ʻoku lahi pē ʻi [[:Category:Haʻapai|Haʻapai]] mo [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]] pē. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 11. ʻOku ne saiʻia ki heʻene tuʻula ʻi ʻolunga ʻo e ngaahi uaea ʻuhila (vakai foki ki he [[pekepekatea]]).
ʻOku lahi ʻenau nofo ʻi he ʻAna pekepeka ʻi [[Kapa]].
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Whiterumped swiftlet |faitā= Whiterumpedswiftlet.jpg |faitālaulahi=280px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[apodiformes]] |familia= [[APODIDAE]] |genus=Aerodramus |species=spodiopygius |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Titian Peale|Peale]], 1848) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''pekepeka tea''' ko e manupuna tuʻufonua ʻi Tongá ni, ka ʻikai ʻi [[:Category:Haʻapai|Haʻapai]]. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 13. ʻOku ʻikai te ne saiʻia ki haʻane tuʻula ʻi ʻolunga ʻo e ngaahi uaea ʻuhila (vakai ki he [[Pekepeka (manupuna)]], ka ʻoku lele pē ʻi he langi, pea nofo ʻi loto he poʻuli ʻo e ngaahi ʻana liku (ko ʻAnahulu ʻi [[Haveluliku]] mo e hā fua).
ʻOku ui foki ko e ''Collocalia spodiopygius'', (''Collocalia spodiopygia'' ?).
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Friendly grounddove |faitā= |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[columbiformes]] |familia= [[COLUMBIDAE]] |genus=Gallicolumba |species=stairi |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[George Robert Gray|G.R. Gray]], 1856) |fehokotaki= cs }} [[Image:Tonga 1998 70s.jpg|left|320px|thumb]] Ko e '''tu''' ko e manupuna tuʻufonua ʻi Tongá ni, ka nofo pē ʻi he vao ʻo e ngaahi motu mamaʻo, ʻa ia ko [[Fonualei (moʻungaafi)]], [[Late]], mo [[Hunga (Haʻapai)]]. Pea ʻoku ne nofo foki ʻi he vao ʻo [[Haʻamoa]], [[Fisi]], [[ʻUvea]] mo [[Futuna]], ka ʻoku siʻisiʻi pē, ʻoku meimei ʻauhamālie.
ʻOku faingataʻa ke te fievākai ki ai, ʻa ia ko hono ʻuhinga ʻe taha ʻi he [[lea fakapilitānia]] ''shy grounddove'' (lupekelekele mā). Ko e ʻuhinga ko e ''Gallicolumba stairii'' ko e sipelahalaʻi ia (ʻa ia naʻe ngāueʻaki ʻe he ʻofisi lītohi). Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 26.
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga *http://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php/40664/all faʻahinga maluʻi fakamāmani {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Crimson crowned fruitdove |hingoa=Kulukulu |faitā= Kulukulu.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[columbiformes]] |familia= [[COLUMBIDAE]] |genus=Ptilinopus |species=porphyraceus |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Coenraad Jacob Temminck|Temminck]], 1821) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''kulukulu''' ko e manupuna tuʻufonua ʻi Tongá ni, nofo ʻi he vao. Pea ʻoku ne nofo foki ʻi [[Haʻamoa]], [[Niuē]], [[Fisi]], [[ʻUvea]], [[Futuna]], mo [[Mikolonisia]]. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 23. ʻOku meimei tatau ʻene ʻasi mo e [[manumaʻa]] fefine. Ko ʻene tangi ko e ''ko-ko...'' (tuʻovalu pe ofi ki ai) ʻoku ʻikai hikihiki tō.
[[File:PtilopusClementinaeKeulemans.jpg|250px]]
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Feral pigeon |faitā= PigeonMonceau.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[columbiformes]] |familia= [[COLUMBIDAE]] |genus=Columba |species=livia |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1789) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''lupe''' ko e manupuna ʻomi ki Tongá ni, ʻoku ne nofo pē ʻi he ngaahi kolo lahi. ʻOku tokua, naʻe ʻomi ʻe he tuʻi ʻi heʻene fiemaʻu ʻa e fanga lupe ʻi he puna matavai ʻi kolo; tatau mo e ngaahi kolo lahi ʻi muli. Naʻe ʻikai puke ia ʻe he vaʻa kolonitini. ʻA ia ʻoku tatau he taimí ni ko Nukuʻalofa mo e ngaahi kolo muli: ko e fanga manupuna taʻefiemaʻu, siko ʻi he ngaahi feituʻu kotoa. Mo e pālasi foki.
Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 30.
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Blue jacaranda, Black poui |faitā=Jacaranda mimosifolia2.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[lamiales]] |familia= [[BIGNONIACEAE]] |genus=Jacaranda |species=mimosifolia |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[David Don|D.Don]] |fehokotaki= cs }} [[File:Jacaranda mimosifolia fruits (opened and closed) 2.jpeg|left|thumb|300px|Ko e ngaahi tenga, tapuni mo e fakaava]] Ko e '''poui''' (hingoa taʻefakalakanga, mei he muli (ʻAmelika tonga?)) ko e fuʻu ʻakau lahi ia, ʻomi ki Tongá ni mei he [[ʻAmelika tonga]] naʻe ʻikai fuoloa. ʻOku lahi mo e fuoloa hono matalaʻiʻakau lanupulū, ʻoku matala (ʻi Tongatapu) lolotonga he [[kilisimasi]].
ʻIlo: Lautohi, ʻĀtele, Tongatapu.
== Tataku == *http://cookislands.bishopmuseum.org/species.asp?id=6285 *http://www.hear.org/pier/species/jacaranda_mimosifolia.htm {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Audubon's shearwater |faitā=Puffinus_subalaris_Galapagos.jpg |faitālaulahi=360px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[Procellariiformes]] |familia= [[PROCELLARIIDAE]] |genus=Puffinus |species=lherminieri |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Rene Primevere Lesson|Lesson]], 1839 |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''teiko''' ko e manupuna ʻo e tuʻafanga ʻi Tongá ni, ʻoku ne fakafānau ʻi ai ([[Niuafoʻou]], [[Late]], [[Hunga (Haʻapai)]], [[ʻAta]])?. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 30, kapakau sm ʻe 69. ʻOku ne tangi ʻi he pō pē.
Ko hono hingoa kakato: ''P. l. dichrous''.
==Tataku== * D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Wedgetailed shearwater |faitā=Wedge tailed shearwater flight.JPG |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[Procellariiformes]] |familia= [[PROCELLARIIDAE]] |genus=Puffinus |species=pacificus |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1789 |fehokotaki= cs }} [[file:Puffinus pacificus MHNT ZOO 2010 11 42 ilot Lagon Nv.Calédonie de Naurois.jpg |thumb|Manuʻuli]] Ko e '''manuʻuli''' ko e manupuna ʻo e tuʻafanga ʻi Tongá ni, ʻoku ne fakafānau ʻi ai lolotonga ʻOkatopa ki he Mē, pea ʻalu. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 43, kapakau sm ʻe 101. Ko e manupuna lahi, ʻoku melomelo fakapōpōʻuli, mo hono iku fuotōtao.
Ko hono ongo ʻuhinga ko e '''[[teiko]]''' pe '''[[lafu]]''', kā ʻoku na ngāueʻaki foki maʻa e ngaahi manupuna kehe.
== Tataku == *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Shorttailed shearwater |faitā=Short-tailed Shearwater.jpg |faitālaulahi=280px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[Procellariiformes]] |familia= [[PROCELLARIIDAE]] |genus=Puffinus |species=tenuirostris |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Coenraad Jacob Temminck|Temminck]], 1835) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e taha ʻo e ngaahi '''lafu''' lahi ia, ko e manupuná ni. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 42, kapakau sm ʻe 98. Ko e manupuna lahi mo hono iku nonou.
ʻOku ne nofo pea fakafānau ʻi he taimi mafana (Tisema mo e hā fua) ʻi [[Tasimani]] pe ofi ki ai ʻi [[ʻAositelēlia]]. ʻI he taimi ʻo e fakanonou ʻa e ngaahi ʻaho ʻoku ne lele ki he tokelau, laka hake ʻi he hihifo ʻo e [[pasifiki]] ki he [[ʻotu motu Aleuti]] mo [[Kamisatika]] ([[Lusia]]). ʻOsi he taimi mafana (Sune mo e hā fua) ʻi hē, ʻoku ne lele ki [[Kalifonia]] pea laka he pasifiki loto ki ʻAositelēlia. ʻA ia ʻoku ne ʻahia pē ʻa e tuʻafanga ʻo Tongá ni lolotonga Sēpitema ki Nōvema.
== Tataku == *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Kermadec petrel |faitā= |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[Procellariiformes]] |familia= [[PROCELLARIIDAE]] |genus=Pterodroma |species=neglecta |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Hermann Schlegel|Schlegel]] 1863) |fehokotaki= s }} Ko e taha ʻo e ngaahi '''lafu''' lahi ia, ko e manupuná ni. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 38, kapakau sm ʻe 100. ʻOku tupu mo fakafānau fakakolonia ʻi [[ʻAta]] pē, ʻa ia hono hingoa.
ʻOku meimei tatau ʻene ʻasi mo e [[lafu fakamelomelo]], kā ʻoku ʻi ai ʻa hono konga hinehina ʻi he loto ʻo hono kapakau.
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Mottled petrel |faitā=Korure Godman.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[Procellariiformes]] |familia= [[PROCELLARIIDAE]] |genus=Pterodroma |species=inexpectata |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Johann Reinhold Forster|J.R. Forster]] 1844) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e taha ʻo e ngaahi '''lafu''' lahi ia, ko e manupuná ni. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 34, kapakau sm ʻe 78. ʻOku ʻaʻahi pē ki Tongá ni taimi ʻe niʻihi, ʻi heʻene folau fakataʻu ki he [[tahi Perengi]] mei [[Nuʻusila]] pea foki.
ʻOku ui ko e ''kōrure'' ʻi he [[lea fakamauli]].
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Wandering albatross |faitā=Wandering Albatross (van Poppel).jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[Procellariiformes]] |familia= [[DIOMEDEIDAE]] |genus=Diomedea |species=exulans |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Carolus Linnaeus|Linnaeus]] 1758 |fehokotaki= cs }} [[File: Grand Albatros MHNT.jpg|thumb|'' Diomedea exulans '']]
Ko e '''katafa''' ko e manupuna lahi taha ʻi Tongá ni mo māmani. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 115, kapakau sm ʻe 330. ʻAuhē, ʻoku ne ʻaʻahi taimi ʻe niʻihi lolotonga he ngataʻanga ʻo Mē ki he kamataʻanga ʻo ʻOkatopa. ʻOku hinehina mo e kiʻi ʻuliʻuli hono fulufulu, kā ʻoku melomelo ko e katafa muimui.
== Tataku == *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Greater frigatebird |faitā=Frigatebird snatch.JPG |faitālaulahi=360px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[Pelecaniformes]] |familia= [[FREGATIDAE]] |genus=Fregata |species=minor |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Johann Friedrich Gmelin|Gmelin]] 1789) |fehokotaki= cs }} [[Image:Great Frigatebird at Genovesa.JPG|left|thumb|300px|helekosi fiehā]] [[File:Fregata minor MHNT.ZOO.2010.11.2.17.jpg|thumb|left| ''Fregata minor'']] Ko e '''lofa''' pe '''helekosi''' ko e manupuna lahi ʻo e tuʻafanga ʻi Tongá ni. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 93, kapakau sm ʻe 218. ʻOku lahi ange ʻa e lofa lalahi ʻi he [[lofa iiki]], neongo hono hingoa ʻi he [[lea fakalatina]]: helekosi siʻi. ʻOku meimei tatau ʻena ʻasi, kā ko e lofa lalahi ʻoku ʻikai ʻi ai ʻa hano konga hinehina ʻi hono fulufulu ʻi ʻolunga. Pea ʻoku toe hono tangai-monga kulokula, ʻoku ngāueʻaki ʻe he manupuna tangata ʻi heʻene fiehā ki he ngaahi fefine.
ʻOku ui ko e ''iwa'' ʻi he [[lea fakahauaiʻi]].
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Tahiti petrel |faitā=Tahitipetrel1.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[Procellariiformes]] |familia= [[PROCELLARIIDAE]] |genus=Pseudobulweria |species=rostrata |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Titian Peale|Peale]] 1848) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e taha ʻo e ngaahi '''lafu''' lahi ia, ko e manupuná ni. ʻOku ʻauhē ʻa e lafu tahisi, ka mahalo pē ʻoku fakafānau ʻe ia ʻi Tongá ni. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 39, kapakau sm ʻe 84.
ʻOku ui foki ko e ''Pterodroma rostrata''.
== Tataku == * D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Sooty tern |faitā=Sterna fuscata.JPG |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[charadriiformes]] |familia= [[LARIDAE]] |genus=Onychoprion |[genus]=tala |species=fuscatus |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Carolus Linnaeus|Linnaeus]] 1766) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''talatā''' pe '''talatahi''' ko e tala ʻe taha ia. Ko e manupuna ʻo e tuʻafanga ʻi Tongá ni, ʻoku lahi ʻene fakafānau ʻi he [[Fonualei (moʻungaafi)|Fonualei]], [[Tokū]] mo e ongo [[Hunga (Haʻapai)|Hunga]], ka ʻoku siʻisiʻi pe ʻene ʻilo ʻi he ngaahi feituʻu kehe. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 43, kapakau sm ʻe 90.
Ko hono ʻuhinga ʻe taha ko e ''Sterna fuscata'' ia. Koʻeni mo e [[tala tuʻalavilavi]] ʻoku na ui ''manutara'' ʻi he [[lea fakalapanui]], pea ʻoku ne ui ko e ''ʻewaʻewa'' ʻi he [[lea fakahauaiʻi]].
== Tataku == * D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Grey-backed tern |faitā=Grey backed tern.JPG |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[charadriiformes]] |familia= [[LARIDAE]] |genus=Onychoprion |[genus]=tala |species=lunatus |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Titian Peale|Peale]] 1848) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''talatā tuʻa lavilavi''' ko e tala ʻe taha ia. Ko e manupuna ʻo e tuʻafanga ʻi Tongá ni, ʻoku tātātaha, ʻoku ne fakafānau ʻi [[Nomuka]] mo e ʻotu Muʻomua pē. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 36, kapakau sm ʻe 74.
Ko hono ʻuhinga ʻe taha ko e ''Sterna lunata'' ia. ʻOku ui ko e ''pakalakala'' ʻi he [[lea fakahauaiʻi]]. Koʻeni mo e [[talatā]] ʻoku na ui ''manutara'' ʻi he [[lea fakalapanui]].
==Tataku== *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Bridled tern |faitā=Bridled Tern LEI Nov06.JPG |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[charadriiformes]] |familia= [[LARIDAE]] |genus=Onychoprion |[genus]=tala |species=anaethetus |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Giovanni Antonio Scopoli|Scopoli]] 1786 |fehokotaki= s }} Ko e '''tala piti''' ko e tala ʻe taha ia. Ko e manupuna ʻo e tuʻafanga ʻi Tongá ni, ʻoku siʻisiʻi pē ʻene ʻasi, ʻoku ne fakafānau ʻi [[:Category:Vavaʻu|Vavaʻu]] mo [[:Category:Tongatapu & takatakai|Tongatapu]]. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 36, kapakau sm ʻe 76. ʻOku meimei tatau ʻene ʻasi mo e [[talatā]], ka ʻoku siʻi maama ange hono fulufulu.
Ko hono ʻuhinga ʻe taha ko e ''Sterna anaethetus '' ia.
== Tataku == * D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Crested tern |faitā=Crested Tern breeding plumage.jpg |regnum= [[monumanu]] |divisio= [[monumanu filo siliva]] |classis= [[manupuna]] |ordo= [[charadriiformes]] |familia= [[LARIDAE]] |genus=Thalasseus |[genus]=tala |species=bergii |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Martin Lichtenstein|Lichtenstein]], 1823) |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''tala lalahi''' ko e tala ʻe taha ia. Ko e manupuna ʻo e tuʻafanga ʻi Tongá ni, ʻoku lahi ʻi he feituʻu kotoa pē, ka ʻoku ʻikai te nau ʻasi tokolahi. Ko hono lahi ko e senitimita ʻe 46, kapakau sm ʻe 104; ko e tala lalahi ia. Ko e meʻa makehe ko hono ngutu engeenga ia mo hono tope ʻuliʻuli ʻoku tomokosi (ʻi he taimi fakafānau).
Ko hono ʻuhinga ʻe taha ko e ''Sterna bergii '' ia.
== Tataku == *D. Watling, Tohi talateu ki he manupuna ʻo Tonga {{potuʻi}}
