Ko e fanga '''Monumanu nofo ʻuta mo vai''' (''amphibia'') ko e pupunga siʻi ia ʻo e ngaahi monumanu veʻefā. ʻOku ʻikai te nau nofo ʻi Tongá ni, ka ʻoku ʻi ai ʻi [[Fisi]] mo [[Haʻamoa]]. Taimi ʻe niʻihi ko e [[poto]] ʻe taha ʻoku ʻomiʻi ki Tonga, ka ʻoku ʻikai fiemaʻu ia.

{{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= Carpenter bee |faitā= Carpenter bee at work.jpg |faitālaulahi= 280px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |phylum= [[veʻehokohoko]] |classis= [[ʻinisēkite]] |subclassis = kapakau |superordo= kapakau tupu ʻi loto |ordo = [[kapakau kalukalu]] |subordo = [[apocrita]] |superfamilia= [[apoidea]] |familia= [[APIDAE]] |genus= Xylocopa |species= |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Latreille]] 1802 |fehokotaki= cs }}
Ko e '''ʻungongo''' ko e ngaahi ʻinisēkite ia, meimei tatau ʻenau ʻasi mo e [[pī hone]], ka ʻoku tafu pea nofo ʻi he ngaahi fuʻu ʻakau (pe nāunau fale).
== Hingoa ʻi he ngaahi lea kehe == *ugogo ([[lea fakafutuna]]) *lago mumu ([[lea fakahaʻamoa]])
== Tataku == *Tongan dictionary; C.M. Churchward *Polynesian classification of small animals; W. Pond; The Weta '''7(4)''' 1984 {{potuʻi}}

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name= Earwig |faitā= Earwig on tin.jpg |faitālaulahi= 280px |regnum= [[monumanu]] |phylum= [[veʻehokohoko]] |classis= [[ʻinisēkite]] |subclassis = kapakau |superordo= kapakau tupu ʻi tuʻa |ordo= '''dermaptera''' |subordo= forficulina |genus= |species= |fakamoʻoniʻanga= [[Charles De Geer|De Geer]] 1773 }}
Ko e '''mokohula''' ko e kiʻi manu ia mo e ongo 'nifo' ʻi mui hono sino.
== Ngaahi faʻahinga kehekehe == * '''kamā''' (ʻi [[Niuatoputapu]]), ''Chelisoches morio'' {black earwig}, ʻoku faʻa ʻilo ʻi he [[fusi|siaine]] moho, ʻoku ne kai ʻa e fanga ane-siaine
== Toe meʻa kehe == {{kananga|Pehē he mokohula ko ia pē ʻoku māʻolunga ʻi lalo tapakau}}
