Naʻa ne kau ki he [[fale alea]] maʻa e kau nōpele ʻo [[ʻEua]]: 1984—1990, pea maʻa e kau nōpele ʻo [[:category:Tongatapu & takatakai|Tongatapu]]: 1990 — pekia.

{| cellpadding="1" style="float: right; border: 1px solid #8888aa; background: #f7f8ff; padding: 5px; font-size: 85%; margin: 0 15px 0 15px;" |<center>[[File:Book of Mormon 1830 edition reprint.jpg|100px]]</center> |- | style="background: #ccf; text-align: center;" | '''Tohi ʻa Molomoná''' |- | * [[ʻUluaki Tohi ʻa Nīfai]] * [[Tohi Hono Ua ʻa Nīfai]] * [[Tohi ʻa Sēkope]] * [[Tohi ʻa ʻĪnosi]] * [[Tohi ʻa Seilomi]] * [[Tohi ʻa ʻAmenai]] * [[Ko e Ngaahi Lea ʻa Molomona]] * [[Tohi ʻa Mōsaia]] * [[Tohi ʻa ʻAlamā]] * [[Tohi ʻa Hilamani]] * [[Ko e Tohi Hono Tolu ʻa Nīfai]] * [[Ko e Tohi Hono Fā ʻa Nīfai]] * [[Tohi ʻa Molomona]] * [[Tohi ʻa ʻEta]] * [[Tohi ʻa Molonai]] |} Ko e '''Tohi ʻa Molomoná''' ko ha tohi ia ʻo e ngaahi folofola māʻoniʻoni ʻoku tatau mo e Tohi Tapú. Ko ha lekooti ia ʻo e ngaahi ngāue ʻa e ʻOtuá mo e kakai naʻa nau nofoʻi ʻa e ongo ʻAmeliká ʻi he kuonga muʻá, pea ʻoku ʻi ai hono kakato ʻo e ongoongolelei taʻengatá.
* [[Siasi Māmonga]] * [[Siosefa Sāmita]] * [http://scriptures.lds.org/to/bm/contents Tohi ʻa Molomoná] * [https://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/tongan/pdf/language-materials/34406_ton.pdf Ko e Tohi ʻa Molomoná PDF] * [https://www.lds.org/scriptures/bofm?lang=ton Ko e Tohi ʻa Molomoná | LDS.org] <br clear=all /><center> {| id="toc" style="margin: 0 2em 0 2em;" ! style="background:#ccccff" align="center" width="100%" colspan="2" | '''Tohi ʻa Molomoná''' |- | align="center" style="font-size: 90%;" colspan="2" |
