Ko e '''Kolisi Petelō Sanele ʻo Kelana''' , ko e ako māʻolunga ʻo e [[Siasi Katolika Loma]] ia.
Naʻe ui ʻe [[Petelō Sanele]], ko e [[maletile]] ia ʻo [[Futuna]]. ʻOku tuʻu ʻi he ʻapi ko Kelana ʻi [[Fungamisi]].

Ko e kau vale ʻoku ʻikai te nau ʻilo ʻa e maletilé ni, ʻoku nau ui ia ko e '''Channel college''', ko e ''kolisi Ava'' ia!

{{potuʻi}}
{{DEFAULTSORT:Petelō Sanele}}
[[Category:Akoʻanga ʻi Tongá ni]]

Ko e '''Takuilau''' , ko e ako māʻolunga ʻo e [[Siasi Katolika Loma]] ia.
ʻOku tuʻu ʻi he ʻapi ko Niukuokai ʻi [[Lapaha]], ʻoku ofi ka ʻoku ʻikai tatau ia mo e Takuilau ʻo onoʻaho, ko e meʻaʻanga ia ʻo e kau Tuʻi Tonga fefine, naʻe hoko he nofoʻanga ʻo e tāupoʻou he ʻaho ni.

Ko e teunga ʻo e fānau ako ko e tupenu pe kofu lanumatapoʻuli ia.

{{potuʻi}}
{{DEFAULTSORT:Takuilau}}
[[Category:Akoʻanga ʻi Tongá ni]]

