{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama=tangata |tamai=[[Mafoaʻaelangi]] |faʻē=Pulimaipauʻu |ʻaho fanauʻi= |ʻaho pekia=1877 |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|ʻAkosita Talefalaʻula||||||||}} |ʻohoana1=Fatai |fānau1= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |}}*http://kitwithers.fortunecity.com/tonga/nobles.html Ko hono hingoa haʻu mei ''Waterhouse'', ko e faifekau naʻe ʻaʻahi ki hono tamai ʻi Niuatoputapu.
Ko e tuʻi ʻo [[Niuatoputapu]] mo [[Tafahi]] ki he 4 Sune 1867, pea naʻa ne ʻoatu ʻa e mafai kia [[Siaosi Tupou I]]. Pea naʻe hoko ia ʻa e nōpele Māʻatu.

