{{Houʻeiki|fakanofo= Vaea |ʻaho fakanofo= ~1775 |ʻaho fakamālōlō= |ki muʻa= [[Vunivalu ʻi Utulangivaka]] |hoko= [[Hivapeaʻulu]] |}}
{{Kāinga ofi|faʻahinga=houʻeiki |maama= tangata |tamai=[[Vunivalu ʻi Utulangivaka]] |faʻē= |ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1775 |ʻaho pekia= |taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} |tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|[[Taulakau]]|Fīnaulahi|Tuʻivakanifisi||||||}} |ʻohoana1=Tāufapōpaofehi |fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Hivapeaʻulu]]|[[Tamataʻane]]|||||||}} |}}*http://kitwithers.fortunecity.com/tonga/nobles.html Ko '''Fīnauhuʻiva''' pe '''Fīnauhuia''' hono hingoa ?
Naʻe ʻi ai ʻa Fīnauhuia ʻe toko2? Vaea: … > Vunivalu > Hafokameʻe I > Fīnauhuʻia I > Hafokameʻe II > Fīnauhuʻia II > Hivapeaʻulu > … ? Ka ko Fīnauhuʻia I ko e foha ʻo Tuʻi Motuliki, ko e foha ʻo [[Muni Fou-halaʻunga]], pea Muni Fīnauhuʻia II ko e tehina ʻo [[Vunivalu ʻi Utulangivaka]] ? *E.W. Gifford, Tongan Society, BPB museum bulletin 61, 1929

