{{Kāinga ofi
|maama=tangata
|tamai=[[Lemeki Taupeamuhu Helu]]
|faʻē= Mele Numia Fuimāono
|ʻaho fanauʻi= ~1860
|ʻaho pekia=
|taʻokete-tokoua= {{tokoua|||||||||}} 
|taʻokete-lau= {{tokoua|||||||||}} 
|tehina-tokoua= {{tokoua|Futaihaʻangana Helu|Sonatane Tāufa Limu|ʻAna Moʻungaelangi||||||}} 
|ʻohoana1= ʻOlivia Kaufusi, mei [[Makāve]], ʻofefine ʻo ʻEpeli Kaufusi
|fānau1= {{tokoua|[[Vili Kaufusi Helu]]||||||||}}
|ʻohoana2= [[Lesieli Mafikovi Tuʻakilaumea]], mei [[Kolomotuʻa]], ʻofefine ʻo Kelepi Tuʻakilaumea
|fānau2= {{tokoua|[[Siosaia Fatai Helu|Siosaia Fatai]]|[[Viliami Tāvao Helu|Viliami Tāvao]]|[[Tēvita ʻOfahemoʻoni Helu|Tēvita ʻOfahemoʻoni]]|Sione Mateaki|Tohi Koula|[[Neomai Latai Taliai (Helu)|Neomai Latai]]|[[Sione Kulī Helu|Sione Kulī]]|Mele Kafoʻatu|Siosifa Holati}}
|}}
[[File:Sioeli-Fangatua-Helu & kāinga.jpg|left|509px|thumb|Sioeli Fangatua Helu mo e kāinga]]
[[File:Sioeli-Fangatua-Helu.jpg|right|300px|thumb|Sioeli Fangatua lolotonga ʻene ako ʻi Kolisi ko Tupou]]
Nofo ʻi [[Foa|Fotua]]. Ko e taʻokete lele ʻo Siosaia ko ʻIlaisa Futa ia, kā naʻa ne mate ʻi muʻa ʻene mali.

Ko Sioeli ko e tangata poto ʻaupito, ko e kāpiteni ia ʻo [[Kolisi ko Tupou]] ʻi 1878, pea naʻa ne kau ki he kalasi makehe ko e [[helohelo]]. Tatau ia mo hono foha ʻe tokofā (Fatai, Viliami Tāvao, Tēvita ʻOfa, Sione Kulī) (naʻe mate kei siʻi ʻa Sione Mateaki mo Siosifa Holati (mo e kiʻi taʻahine ko Tohi Koula)).
*Genealogy of ʻIlaisa Futaʻihaʻangana Helu, http://histfam.familysearch.org/oralhistories/getperson.php?personID=I7&tree=IlaisaHelu

