ʻOku tala ʻe he taha, ko '''Fusipala''' ko ʻene fehuhu ia.

{{Puha fakafaʻahinga |name=Bronze-leaved clerodendrum |faitā=Clerodendrum quadriloculare at Fairchild Tropical Botanical Garden.jpg |regnum= [[ʻakau]] |divisio= [[ʻakau matala]] |classis= [[lautengaʻiua]] |ordo= [[lamiales]] |familia= [[VERBENACEAE]] |genus=Clerodendrum |species=quadriloculare |fakamoʻoniʻanga= ([[Francisco Manuel Blanco|Blanco]]) [[Merr.]] |fehokotaki= cs }} Ko e '''tutuhina lau polōnise''' (hingoa taʻefakalakanga, mei he [[lea fakapilitānia]]), pe '''ʻone ulo''' ko e fuʻu ʻakau siʻi ia, ʻoku tupu ʻi he ngoue Tonga ʻi heʻene ʻasi fakaʻofoʻofa. Ka ko e meʻa fakafaingataʻa ʻaupito haʻane taʻakifuʻu, ʻa ia ʻoku fehiʻa ki ai ʻa e kolonitini.
Ko e ʻakau naʻe ʻomi ki Tonga mei [[Papua-niu-kini]] mo e [[Filipaine]], naʻe ʻikai fuoloa. Tatau mo e toenga ʻo [[Polinisia]], ʻa ia ʻoku ʻikai ʻi ai hano hingoa taukei.
==Tataku== [http://www.hear.org/pier/species/clerodendrum_quadriloculare.htm] Pacific Island Ecosystems at Risk {{potuʻi}}

Naʻe fakanofo ko e ([[:Category:Nōpele|nōpele]]) Taumoepeau-Tupou mei [[Toula]] mo [[Kotu]] ʻi 5 ʻEpeleli 2011.

